                            g      += 1;

                            maxAge += 1;

                                return;

            var WRInitTime = (new Date()).getTime();
            var o_scr = document.getElementsByTagName("script");
            var i_scrptCnt = 0;
            var s_proto = window.location.protocol;
            var s_domain = (s_proto == "https:")
                ? "a248.e.akamai.net/f/248/5879/1h/i.travelpn.com"
                : "i.travelpn.com.edgesuite.net";
            for (i = 0; i < o_scr.length; i += 1) {
                var s_scriptSrc = o_scr
                    .item(i)
                    .src;
                i_scrptCnt += parseInt((s_scriptSrc.toUpperCase().indexOf("NAVIGATION.JS") > 0)
                    ? "1"
                    : "0");
            }
            if (i_scrptCnt == 0) {
                var o_head = document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0];
                var o_script = document.createElement("script");
                o_script.type = "text/javascript";
                o_script.src  = s_proto + "//" + s_domain + "/js/navigation.js";
                o_head.appendChild(o_script);
            }

            function Collapsible(oEl, triggerEl, dState, callback) {
                var __c = this,
                    Show,
                    Hide;
                __c.state    = (typeof(dState) === "undefined")
                    ? 0
                    : dState;
                __c.Trigger  = function () {
                    (__c.state === 0)
                        ? Show()
                        : Hide();
                };
                __c.SetUp    = function () {
                    (__c.state === 0)
                        ? Hide(1)
                        : Show(1);
                };
                __c.callback = callback;
                Show         = function (cb) {
                    $(oEl).removeClass("inactive hide");
                    __c.state = 1;
                    if (typeof(callback) == "object" && typeof(cb) == "undefined") {
                        callback
                            .fn
                            .call(this, callback.params);
                    }
                };
                Hide         = function () {
                    $(oEl).addClass("inactive hide");
                    __c.state = 0;
                    if (typeof(callback) == "object") {
                        callback
                            .fn
                            .call(this, callback.params);
                    }
                };
                if ($(triggerEl).length) {
                    $(triggerEl)
                        .bind("click", function () {
                            __c.Trigger();
                            if (jQuery(triggerEl).attr("nodeName") === "A") {
                                return false;
                            }
                        });
                }
                __c.SetUp();
            }

                        ? "none"
                        : (i_nBdisplay == 1)
                            ? "block"
                            : "inline";
                }

            function SetCookie(cookieName, cookieValue, nDays) {
                var today = new Date();
                var expire = new Date();
                if (nDays == null || nDays == 0) {
                    nDays = 1;
                }
                expire.setTime(today.getTime() + 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000 * nDays);
                document.cookie = cookieName + "=" + escape(cookieValue) + ";expires=" + expire.toGMTString();
            }
            function GetCookie(Name) {
                var search = Name + "=";
                var returnvalue = "";
                if (document.cookie.length > 0) {
                    offset = document
                        .cookie
                        .indexOf(search);
                    if (offset != -1) {
                        offset += search.length;
                        end    = document
                            .cookie
                            .indexOf(";", offset);
                        if (end == -1) {
                            end = document.cookie.length;
                        }
                        returnvalue = unescape(document.cookie.substring(offset, end));
                    }
                }
                return returnvalue;
            }

                    } else {

                            SetCookie("popunder", "yes", "1");
                            //loadpopunder(o_form);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // The following js comes from: http://i.travelpn.com/js/jquery_tvly.js //
            (function ($) {
                $.fn.tvly            = {};
                $.tvly               = {
                    loadCSS   : function (url, callback) {
                        var css = document.createElement("link");
                        css.type = "text/css";
                        css.rel  = "stylesheet";
                        css.href = url;
                        var head = document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0] || document.documentElement;
                        head.appendChild(css);
                        if (callback) {
                            callback();
                        }
                    },
                    loadScript: function (scripts, callback) {
                        var lastScriptIndex       = scripts.length - 1,
                            numberOfScriptsLoaded = 0,
                            scriptLoaded          = false;
                        $.each(scripts, function (index, url) {
                            var script = document.createElement("script");
                            script.type = "text/javascript";
                            script.src  = url;
                            if (script.readyState) {
                                script.onreadystatechange = function () {
                                    if (script.readyState == "loaded" || script.readyState == "complete") {
                                        script.onreadystatechange = null;
                                        numberOfScriptsLoaded     += 1;
                                        if (callback && numberOfScriptsLoaded === scripts.length) {
                                            callback();
                                        }
                                    }
                                };
                            } else {
                                script.onload = function () {
                                    numberOfScriptsLoaded += 1;
                                    if (callback && numberOfScriptsLoaded === scripts.length) {
                                        callback();
                                    }
                                };
                            }
                            var head = document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0] || document.documentElement;
                            head.appendChild(script);
                        });
                    }
                };
                $.fn.tvly.loadScript = $.tvly.loadScript;
                $.fn.tvly.loadCSS    = $.tvly.loadCSS;
                $.tvly.HoptoadLogger = (function () {
                    var defaults = {
                        environment_name: "production",
                        hoptoadsrc      : (("https:" == document.location.protocol)
                            ? "https://"
                            : "http://") + "airbrakeapp.com/javascripts/notifier.js"
                    };
                    var _hoptoadlogger = function (options) {
                        this.initialize(options);
                    };
                    _hoptoadlogger.prototype = {
                        initialize    : function (options) {
                            var oScope = this;
                            var console;
                            if (typeof window.console === "undefined") {
                                console = {
                                    log: function () {}
                                };
                            } else {
                                console = window.console;
                            }
                            oScope.console = console;
                            var _error_defaults = {
                                action   : "",
                                component: "",
                                url      : window.location.href
                            };
                            _error_defaults         = $.extend(_error_defaults, options.error_defaults);
                            defaults.error_defaults = _error_defaults;
                            delete options.error_defaults;
                            this.options = $.extend(defaults, options);
                            if (typeof(Hoptoad) == "undefined") {
                                jQuery(document)
                                    .bind("hoptoad::loaded", function () {
                                        oScope
                                            .onScriptLoaded
                                            .apply(oScope, arguments);
                                    });
                                if (this.options && this.options.hoptoadsrc) {
                                    $
                                        .tvly
                                        .loadScript([this.options.hoptoadsrc], function () {
                                            jQuery(document).trigger("hoptoad::loaded", [oScope]);
                                        });
                                }
                            } else {
                                oScope.onScriptLoaded(null, oScope);
                            }
                        },
                        onScriptLoaded: function (e, logger) {
                            Hoptoad.setEnvironment(this.options.environment_name);
                            Hoptoad.setHost(this.options.host);
                            Hoptoad.setKey(this.options.key);
                            Hoptoad.setErrorDefaults(this.options.error_defaults);
                            (function () {
                                var proxied = window.onerror;
                                window.onerror = function (message, file, line) {
                                    logger
                                        .console
                                        .log(message + " " + file + " " + line);
                                    return proxied.apply(this, arguments);
                                };
                            })();
                        },
                        write         : function (message, file, line) {
                            setTimeout(function () {
                                Hoptoad.notify({
                                    message: message,
                                    stack  : "()@" + (file
                                        ? file + ":"
                                        : "") + (line || "")
                                });
                            }, 100);
                        }
                    };
                    return _hoptoadlogger;
                })();
                $.tvly.Logger        = (function () {
                    var ConsoleDevice = function (options) {
                        this.initialize(options);
                    };
                    ConsoleDevice.prototype = {
                        initialize: function (options) {
                            var console;
                            if (typeof window.console === "undefined") {
                                console = {
                                    log: function () {}
                                };
                            } else {
                                console = window.console;
                            }
                            this.console = console;
                        },
                        write     : function (message, file, line) {
                            console.log(message + (file
                                ? " file: " + file
                                : "") + (line
                                ? " line: " + line
                                : ""));
                        }
                    };
                    var _Severity       = {
                            DEBUG  : 0,
                            ERROR  : 3,
                            FATAL  : 4,
                            INFO   : 1,
                            UNKNOWN: 5,
                            WARN   : 2
                        },
                        format_severity = function (severity) {
                            var _s = "";
                            switch (severity) {
                                case 0:
                                    _s = "DEBUG";
                                    break;
                                case 1:
                                    _s = "INFO";
                                    break;
                                case 2:
                                    _s = "WARN";
                                    break;
                                case 3:
                                    _s = "ERROR";
                                    break;
                                case 4:
                                    _s = "FATAL";
                                    break;
                                case 5:
                                    _s = "UNKNOWN";
                                    break;
                                default:
                                    _s = "ANY";
                            }
                            return _s;
                        },
                        format_message  = function (severity, time, progname, msg) {
                            var _time = "";
                            return (severity + " " + progname + " " + _time + ": " + msg);
                        };
                    var _logger = function (options) {
                        this.Severity = _Severity;
                        this.initialize(options);
                    };
                    _logger.prototype = {
                        add            : function (severity, message, progname, file, line) {
                            var severity = severity !== null
                                ? severity
                                : _Severity.UNKNOWN;
                            if (this._logdev == null || severity < this._level) {
                                return true;
                            }
                            var progname = progname || this._progname;
                            if (message == null) {
                                message  = progname;
                                progname = this._progname;
                            }
                            this
                                ._logdev
                                .write(format_message(format_severity(severity), new Date(), progname, message), file, line);
                            return true;
                        },
                        debug          : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.DEBUG, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        error          : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.ERROR, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        fatal          : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.FATAL, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        getProgName    : function () {
                            return this._progname;
                        },
                        getSevThreshold: function () {
                            return this._level;
                        },
                        info           : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.INFO, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        initialize     : function (options) {
                            this._progname = options && options.progname
                                ? options.progname
                                : "";
                            this._level    = options && options.sev_threshold
                                ? options.sev_threshold
                                : _Severity.ERROR;
                            this._logdev   = options && options.logdev
                                ? options.logdev
                                : new ConsoleDevice();
                            var logger = this;
                            logger.info("tvly javascript logger v0.1a enabled...");
                        },
                        log            : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.DEBUG, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        setProgName    : function (progname) {
                            this._progname = progname;
                        },
                        setSevThreshold: function (level) {
                            this._level = level;
                        },
                        unknown        : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.UNKNOWN, null, progname, file, line);
                        },
                        warn           : function (progname, file, line) {
                            return this.add(_Severity.WARN, null, progname, file, line);
                        }
                    };
                    return _logger;
                })();
            })(jQuery); // .
