            }
            jQuery.tvly.Cannonball           = function (options) {
                if ($(".cb-nav-form input[name='nav']:checked").length == 0) {
                    selectedNav = $($(".cb-nav-form input[name='nav']")[0]);
                    selectedNav.attr("checked", "checked");
                }
                this.initialize(options);
            };
            jQuery.tvly.Cannonball.prototype = {
                _bindEvents     : function (cb) {
                    $("form", this.options.cb).bind("submit", {
                        cb: this
                    }, this.checkForm.init);
                },
                _changeView     : function (event) {
                    var cb = event.data.cb;
                    cb.hideError();
                    $("." + cb.options.currentView).css("display", "none");
                    cb.options.currentView = $(this).val();
                    switch ($(this).val()) {
                        case "form-co":
                            cb
                                .cars
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-hcx":
                            cb
                                .hcx
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-ro":
                            cb
                                .rail
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-fh":
                        case "form-fhc":
                        case "form-fhcyo":
                            cb
                                .flighthotel
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-fo":
                        case "form-fow":
                            cb
                                .flights
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-ho":
                            cb
                                .hotels
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-cro":
                            cb
                                .cruise
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                        case "form-act":
                            cb
                                .activities
                                .init(cb);
                            break;
                    }
                },
                _maintainState  : function (event) {
                    var data = $.extend(true, {
                        cb    : "",
                        item  : "",
                        method: "CLASS"
                    }, event.data);
                    switch (data.method) {
                        case "SELECT_NAME":
                            $("select[name='" + $(this).attr("name") + "']").val($(this).val());
                            break;
                        default:
                            $(data.item, data.cb.options.cb).val($(event.currentTarget).val());
                    }
                },
                _prepAir        : function () {},
                _prepCars       : function (cb) {},
                _prepHotels     : function () {},
                _prepTrip       : function () {},
                _startCannonball: function () {},
                activities      : {
                    init: function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-act");
                        __cb.show();
                        cb.options.Service = $("input[name='Service']", cb.options.cb).val();
                        if (!cb.activities.ready) {
                            jQuery.extend(true, cb.options.datePicker, {
                                fromID : "act-start",
                                onError: cb.checkDates,
                                toID   : "act-thru"
                            });
                            $(".cb-fromdate, .cb-todate", __cb).datepicker(cb.options.datePicker);
                            cb.activities.ready = true;
                        }
                        if (jQuery("#nav-pd").attr("checked")) {
                            jQuery("#popular-dest-dropdown").css("display", "");
                            jQuery("#act-destinations").removeAttr("disabled");
                            jQuery("#enter-dest-field").css("display", "none");
                            jQuery("#act_citytext").attr("disabled", "disabled");
                        } else {
                            jQuery("#enter-dest-field").css("display", "");
                            jQuery("#act_citytext").removeAttr("disabled");
                            jQuery("#popular-dest-dropdown").css("display", "none");
                            jQuery("#act-destinations").attr("disabled", "disabled");
                        }
                        $("input[type='checkbox']", cb.options.cb)
                            .each(function () {
                                if (typeof($.data(jQuery(this).get(0), "events")) === "undefined") {
                                    if (jQuery(this).attr("name") != "ACTTYPE_all") {
                                        jQuery(this)
                                            .click(function () {
                                                jQuery("#acttype0").attr("checked", false);
                                            });
                                    } else {
                                        jQuery(this)
                                            .click(function () {
                                                $("input[type='checkbox']", cb.options.cb)
                                                    .each(function () {
                                                        jQuery(this).attr("checked", false);
                                                    });
                                                jQuery("#acttype0").attr("checked", true);
                                            });
                                    }
                                }
                            });
                        if (typeof($.data($("#nav-ed").get(0), "events").change) === "undefined") {
                            jQuery("#nav-ed")
                                .change(function () {
                                    jQuery("#popular-dest-dropdown").css("display", "none");
                                    jQuery("#enter-dest-field").css("display", "");
                                });
                        }
                    }
                },
                cars            : {
                    bindEvents    : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-co");
                        $(".cb-pick-location", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-pick-location"
                        }, cb._maintainState).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-pick-location"
                        }, cb.cars.changeLocation);
                        $(".cb-co-discount", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromdate"
                        }, cb.cars.frequentRenter);
                        $(".cb-fromdate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromdate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-todate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-todate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-fromtime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromtime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-totime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-totime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-to-city", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-to-city"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-state", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-state"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-country", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-country"
                        }, cb._maintainState).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-country"
                        }, cb.cars.countryScope);
                        $(".cb-car-type", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-car-type"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                    },
                    changeLocation: function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("." + event.data.cb.options.currentView);
                        $(".cb-near-airport", __cb).show();
                        $("option", this).each(function () {
                            var val = $(this).val();
                            if ($(this).attr("selected")) {
                                if (val == "pu_air") {
                                    $(".cb-near-airport", __cb).hide();
                                }
                                $("." + val, __cb).show();
                            } else {
                                $("." + val, __cb).hide();
                            }
                        });
                    },
                    countryScope  : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("." + event.data.cb.options.currentView);
                        switch ($(this).val()) {
                            case "US":
                            case "CA":
                                $(".cb-state-row", __cb).show();
                                break;
                            default:
                                $(".cb-state-row", __cb).hide();
                        }
                    },
                    frequentRenter: function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("." + event.data.cb.options.currentView);
                        switch ($(this).val()) {
                            case "ZR":
                                oDisc = "Corporate Discount #:";
                                oID   = "Dollar Express #:";
                                break;
                            case "ZT":
                                oDisc = "Corporate Discount #:";
                                oID   = "Blue Chip #:";
                                break;
                            case "AL":
                                oDisc = "Corporate Discount #:";
                                oID   = "Quicksilver ID:";
                                break;
                            case "ZL":
                                oDisc = "Corporate Discount #:";
                                oID   = "Emerald Club ID:";
                                break;
                            case "ZA":
                                oDisc = "Corporate Discount #:";
                                oID   = "Payless Perks #:";
                                break;
                            case "ZI":
                                oDisc = "AWD #:";
                                oID   = "Wizard #:";
                                break;
                            case "ZD":
                                oDisc = "BCD #:";
                                oID   = "Fast Break #:";
                                break;
                            case "EP":
                                oDisc = "Contract #:";
                                oID   = "Priviledge #:";
                                break;
                            case "ZE":
                                oDisc = "CDP:";
                                oID   = "Hertz #1 Club:";
                                break;
                            case "ET":
                                oDisc = "Customer #:";
                                oID   = "Enterprise Plus #:";
                                break;
                            case "AD":
                                oDisc = "Discount Code:";
                                oID   = false;
                                break;
                            case "EZ":
                                oDisc = false;
                                oID   = "E-Z Money #:";
                                break;
                            case "FX":
                                oDisc = "Fox Corporate #:";
                                oID   = "Fox Rewards:";
                                break;
                            case "ZP":
                                oDisc = false;
                                oID   = false;
                                var noRates = true;
                                break;
                            case "ZH":
                                oDisc = "Discount Number:";
                                oID   = false;
                                break;
                            case "":
                                oDisc = false;
                                oID   = false;
                                break;
                        }
                        if (oDisc) {
                            $("label", ".cb-disc-name").text(oDisc);
                            $(".cb-disc-name", __cb).show();
                        } else {
                            $(".cb-disc-name", __cb).hide();
                        }
                        if (oID) {
                            $("label", ".cb-disc-id").text(oID);
                            $(".cb-disc-id", __cb).show();
                        } else {
                            $(".cb-disc-id", __cb).hide();
                        }
                    },
                    init          : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-co");
                        __cb.show();
                        cb.options.Service = $("input[name='Service']", cb.options.cb).val();
                        if (!cb.cars.ready) {
                            jQuery.extend(true, cb.options.datePicker, {
                                fromID : "co-fromdate",
                                onError: cb.checkDates,
                                toID   : "co-todate"
                            });
                            $(".cb-fromdate, .cb-todate", __cb).datepicker(cb.options.datePicker);
                            cb
                                .cars
                                .bindEvents(cb);
                            cb.cars.ready = true;
                        }
                        $(".cb-to-city,.cb-pick-location,.countryScope,.cb-country,.cb-co-discount,.cb-from" +
                                "date, .cb-todate,.cb-state,.cb-car-type",
                        __cb).trigger("change");
                    },
                    ready         : false
                },
                checkForm       : {
                    cb            : null,
                    characters    : function () {},
                    checkChildAges: function (form) {
                        var e         = -1,
                            el        = null,
                            irooms,
                            childages = 0,
                            children  = $(".cb-children", form),
                            i         = 0;
                        var adults  = $("#fo-adults", form),
                            seniors = $("#fo-seniors", form);
                        switch (this.cb.options.currentView) {
                            case "form-fo":
                            case "form-fow":
                                var checkAllMinorAges = false;
                                if (adults.val() == "0" && seniors.val() == "0") {
                                    checkAllMinorAges = true;
                                }
                                if (children.val() != 0) {
                                    childages = $(".cb-child-ages select", form);
                                    for (i = 0; i < children.val(); i += 1) {
                                        if (isNaN($(childages[i]).val())) {
                                            e = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_child;
                                            return {
                                                element: $(childages[i]),
                                                error  : e
                                            };
                                        } else {
                                            if (checkAllMinorAges) {
                                                if ($(childages[i]).val() < 15) {
                                                    e = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_child_unaccompanied;
                                                    return {
                                                        element: $(childages[i]),
                                                        error  : e
                                                    };
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                break;
                            default:
                                var roomchildages = $(".cb-room-child-ages", form);
                                irooms = $(".cb-total-rooms", form)
                                    ? $(".cb-total-rooms", form).val()
                                    : 1;
                                for (i = 0; i < irooms; i += 1) {
                                    if ($(children[i]).val() != 0) {
                                        for (var j = 0; j < $(children[i]).val(); j += 1) {
                                            childages = $("select", $(roomchildages[i]));
                                            if (isNaN($(childages[j]).val())) {
                                                e = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_child;
                                                return {
                                                    element: $(childages[j]),
                                                    error  : e
                                                };
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                        }
                        return {element: el, error: e};
                    },
                    checkDates    : function (form) {
                        var e  = -1,
                            el = null,
                            pe = null;
                        var ret = $(".cb-fromdate", form).datepicker("validate", null, true);
                        if (ret.error) {
                            switch (ret.error) {
                                case "dateIsEmpty":
                                    e  = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_dp_dateinvalid;
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    break;
                                case "return_before_depart":
                                    e  = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_date;
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    break;
                                case "range_longer_than_allowed":
                                    switch (this.cb.options.currentView) {
                                        case "form-fh":
                                        case "form-fhc":
                                        case "form-fo":
                                            e = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_date_range_vac;
                                            break;
                                        case "form-hcx":
                                        case "form-ho":
                                            e = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_date_range_hot;
                                            break;
                                    }
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    if (this.cb.options.currentView == "form-fo" && this.cb.options.flightXsell != true) {
                                        e  = -1,
                                        el = null;
                                    }
                                    break;
                                case "not_A_Date":
                                    e  = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_dp_dateinvalid;
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    break;
                                case "depart_before_allowed_min_date":
                                    e  = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_dp_dateinvalid;
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    break;
                                case "return_after_allowed_max_date":
                                    e  = this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_dp_dateinvalid;
                                    el = $("#" + ret.fieldID, form);
                                    break;
                            }
                            pe = ret.error;
                        }
                        if (ret.error && this.cb.options.currentView == "form-fow") {
                            if (ret.fieldID != $(".cb-fromdate", form).attr("id")) {
                                e  = -1,
                                el = null;
                            }
                        }
                        return {element: el, error: e, picker_e: pe};
                    },
                    checkLength   : function (value, msg, min, max) {
                        var e  = -1,
                            el = null;
                        var _minl = (min || this.cb.options.validateRules.length.min);
                        var _maxl = (max || this.cb.options.validateRules.length.max);
                        if (value.length < _minl || value.length > this.cb.options.validateRules.length._maxl) {
                            return (msg || this.cb.options.errorMsg.e_length);
                        } else {
                            return -1;
                        }
                    },
                    init          : function (event) {
                        var form   = $(this),
                            submit = true,
                            cb     = event.data.cb,
                            e      = -1;
                        cb.checkForm.cb = cb;
                        s_popFlag       = 1;
                        switch (form.attr("id")) {
                            case "cb-form-co":
                                switch ($(".cb-pick-location", form).val()) {
                                    case "pu_addr":
                                        if ($("#co-city", form).length >= 1) {
                                            e = cb
                                                .checkForm
                                                .checkLength($("#co-city", form).val(), cb.options.errorMsg.e_missing_info);
                                            if (e != -1) {
                                                return cb.showError(e, $("#co-city", form));
                                            }
                                        }
                                        if ($("#co-geostate", form).length >= 1) {
                                            if ($("#co-geostate", form).is(":visible")) {
                                                e = cb
                                                    .checkForm
                                                    .checkLength($("#co-geostate", form).val(), cb.options.errorMsg.e_missing_info, 2);
                                                if (e != -1) {
                                                    return cb.showError(e, $("#co-geostate", form));
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                        break;
                                    case "pu_poi":
                                        if ($("#co-interest", form).length >= 1) {
                                            e = cb
                                                .checkForm
                                                .checkLength($("#co-interest", form).val(), cb.options.errorMsg.e_missing_info);
                                            if (e != -1) {
                                                return cb.showError(e, $("#co-interest", form));
                                            }
                                        }
                                        if ($("#co-poistate", form).length >= 1) {
                                            e = cb
                                                .checkForm
                                                .checkLength($("#co-poistate", form).val(), cb.options.errorMsg.e_missing_info, 2);
                                            if (e != -1) {
                                                return cb.showError(e, $("#co-poistate", form));
                                            }
                                        }
                                        break;
                                    case "pu_air":
                                        e = cb
                                            .checkForm
                                            .checkLength($(".cb-to-city", form).val());
                                        if (e != -1) {
                                            return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-to-city", form));
                                        }
                                        break;
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkDates(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    if (e.picker_e == "return_before_depart") {
                                        e.error = cb.options.errorMsg.e_cardate;
                                    }
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "cb-form-hcx":
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkLength($(".cb-to-city", form).val());
                                if (e != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-to-city", form));
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkDates(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    if (e.picker_e == "return_before_depart") {
                                        e.error = cb.options.errorMsg.e_hoteldate;
                                    }
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkChildAges(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "cb-form-fh":
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkLength($(".cb-from", form).val());
                                if (e != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-from", form));
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkLength($(".cb-to", form).val());
                                if (e != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-to", form));
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkDates(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkChildAges(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "cb-form-fo":
                                if ($(".cb-from", form).length != 0) {
                                    e = cb
                                        .checkForm
                                        .checkLength($(".cb-from", form).val());
                                    if (e != -1) {
                                        return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-from", form));
                                    }
                                }
                                if ($(".cb-to", form).length != 0) {
                                    e = cb
                                        .checkForm
                                        .checkLength($(".cb-to", form).val());
                                    if (e != -1) {
                                        return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-to", form));
                                    }
                                }
                                if ($("input[name='dateTypeSelect']:checked", form).val() != "flexibleDates") {
                                    e = cb
                                        .checkForm
                                        .checkDates(form);
                                    if (e.error != -1) {
                                        return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                    }
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkChildAges(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "cb-form-ho":
                                if ($(".cb-total-rooms", form).val() == "5+") {
                                    _gaq.push(["_trackEvent", "ExitLinks", "5orMoreRms", "HFD"]);
                                    cb
                                        .hotels
                                        .searchGroup(cb, form);
                                    return false;
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkLength($(".cb-to-city", form).val());
                                if (e != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e, $(".cb-to-city", form));
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkDates(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    if (e.picker_e == "return_before_depart") {
                                        e.error = cb.options.errorMsg.e_hoteldate;
                                    }
                                    if ($(".cb-ts-hotels:checked", form).length == 1) {
                                        return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                    } else {
                                        if (e.picker_e != "dateIsEmpty" && e.picker_e != "not_A_Date") {
                                            return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkChildAges(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "cb-form-act":
                                s_popFlag = 0;
                                if (jQuery("#nav-pd").attr("checked")) {
                                    e = cb
                                        .checkForm
                                        .checkLength($("#act-destinations", form).val(), "Please select a destination from the drop down below.");
                                    if (e != -1) {
                                        return cb.showError(e, $("#act-destinations", form));
                                    }
                                } else {
                                    if (jQuery("#nav-ed").attr("checked")) {
                                        e = cb
                                            .checkForm
                                            .checkLength($("#act_citytext", form).val());
                                        if (e != -1) {
                                            return cb.showError(e, $("#act_citytext", form));
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                e = cb
                                    .checkForm
                                    .checkDates(form);
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    if (e.picker_e == "return_before_depart") {
                                        e.error = cb.options.errorMsg.e_hoteldate;
                                    } else {
                                        if (e.picker_e != "dateIsEmpty" && e.picker_e != "not_A_Date") {
                                            return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                if (e.error != -1) {
                                    return cb.showError(e.error, e.element);
                                }
                                break;
                        }
                        if ((tvly.service == "TRAVELOCITY") || (tvly.service == "CJUS") || (tvly.service == "TCYCA") || (tvly.service == "CJCA")) {
                            loadPopOrNot(true, s_popFlag, this);
                        }
                        if (cb.options.currentView == "form-fhcyo") {
                            var dep = $(".cb-fromdate", form).datepicker("getDate"),
                                ret = $(".cb-todate", form).datepicker("getDate");
                            $("input[name='dateLeavingMonth']", form).val(dep.getMonth() + 1);
                            $("input[name='dateLeavingDay']", form).val(dep.getDate());
                            $("input[name='dateReturningMonth']", form).val(ret.getMonth() + 1);
                            $("input[name='dateReturningDay']", form).val(ret.getDate());
                        }
                        if (cb.options.flightXsell == true) {
                            $(".cb-fh-submit-button", form).html("Search");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", form).html("Search");
                        }
                        cb.gaTracking(form.attr("id"));
                        return true;
                    }
                },
                cruise          : {
                    init       : function (cb) {
                        $(".form-cro").show();
                        cb.options.Service = $("input[name='Service']", cb.options.cb).val();
                        if (!cb.cruise.ready) {
                            $
                                .getScript(cb.options.cruiseScript, function () {
                                    cb
                                        .cruise
                                        .scriptReady(cb);
                                });
                        }
                    },
                    ready      : false,
                    scriptReady: function (cb) {
                        var dataSource = tvly.wwwDomain + "/js/cb_cruise_svc";
                        new jQuery
                            .tvly
                            .CB
                            .cruise({
                                dataSource   : {
                                    url: dataSource
                                },
                                formId       : "#form-cro",
                                maintainItems: [
                                    "#cruiseLength", "#cru-datemonth", "#departurePort", "#cro-cruiseline"
                                ],
                                selectId     : {
                                    Months: "#cru-datemonth"
                                }
                            });
                        cb.cruise.ready = true;
                    }
                },
                flighthotel     : {
                    bindEvents: function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fh");
                        $(".cb-fromdate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromdate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-todate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-todate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-fromtime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromtime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-totime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-totime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-to-city", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-to-city"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-from-city", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-from-city"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-total-rooms", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-total-rooms"
                        }, cb.hotels.changeRooms).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-total-rooms"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-children", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-children"
                        }, cb.hotels.showChildAges).bind("change", {
                            cb    : cb,
                            item  : ".cb-children",
                            method: "SELECT_NAME"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-room-child-ages select", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb    : cb,
                            item  : ".cb-room-child-ages select",
                            method: "SELECT_NAME"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                    },
                    init      : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fh");
                        __cb.show();
                        cb.options.Service = $("input[name='Service']", __cb).val();
                        switch (cb.options.currentView) {
                            case "form-fhc":
                                document
                                    .getElementById("fh-pkg")
                                    .setAttribute("disabled", "disabled");
                                $("#fhc-pkg").removeAttr("disabled");
                                $(".cb-fhc-message", __cb).show();
                                break;
                            default:
                                document
                                    .getElementById("fhc-pkg")
                                    .setAttribute("disabled", "disabled");
                                $("#fh-pkg").removeAttr("disabled");
                                $(".cb-fhc-message", __cb).hide();
                        }
                        if (!cb.flighthotel.ready) {
                            jQuery.extend(true, cb.options.datePicker, {
                                fromID  : "fh-fromdate",
                                maxRange: 26,
                                onError : cb.checkDates,
                                toID    : "fh-todate"
                            });
                            $(".cb-fromdate, .cb-todate", __cb).datepicker(cb.options.datePicker);
                            cb
                                .flighthotel
                                .bindEvents(cb);
                            cb.flighthotel.ready = true;
                        }
                        $(".cb-to-city,.cb-from-city,.cb-fromdate, .cb-todate,.cb-total-rooms,.cb-children," +
                                ".cb-room-child-ages select",
                        __cb).trigger("change");
                    },
                    ready     : false
                },
                flights         : {
                    advancedSearch   : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        s = event
                            .data
                            .cb
                            .flights
                            .collectForm(event);
                        s += "&leavingFrom=" + $("input[name='leavingFrom']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&goingTo=" + $("input[name='goingTo']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&leavingDate=" + $("input[name='leavingDate']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&dateLeavingTime=" + $("select[name='dateLeavingTime']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&returningDate=" + $("input[name='returningDate']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&dateReturningTime=" + $("select[name='dateReturningTime']", __cb).val();
                        $(this).attr("href", $(this).attr("href") + s);
                    },
                    bindEvents       : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        $(".cb-multi-dest a", __cb).bind("click", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.multiDestSearch);
                        $(".cb-advanced a", __cb).bind("click", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.advancedSearch);
                        $(".cb-fh-submit-button", __cb).bind("click", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.searchFlightHotel);
                        $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).bind("click", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.searchFlights);
                        $(".cb-fromdate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromdate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-todate", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-todate"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-fromtime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-fromtime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-totime", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-totime"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-to-city", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-to-city"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-from-city", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-from-city"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-children", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb  : cb,
                            item: ".cb-children"
                        }, cb.flights.showChildAges).bind("change", {
                            cb    : cb,
                            item  : ".cb-children",
                            method: "SELECT_NAME"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $(".cb-child-ages select", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb    : cb,
                            item  : ".cb-child-ages select",
                            method: "SELECT_NAME"
                        }, cb._maintainState);
                        $("input[name='dateTypeSelect']", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.dateType);
                        $(".cb-csa input", __cb).bind("change", {
                            cb: cb
                        }, cb.flights.compareAirports);
                    },
                    collectForm      : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo"),
                            s    = "";
                        s += "&flightType=multicity";
                        s += "&dateTypeSelect=" + $("input[name='dateTypeSelect']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&goingTo=" + $("input[name='goingTo']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&adults=" + $("select[name='adults']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&children=" + $("select[name='children']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&seniors=" + $("select[name='seniors']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&minorsAge0=" + $("select[name='minorsAge0']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&minorsAge1=" + $("select[name='minorsAge1']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&minorsAge2=" + $("select[name='minorsAge2']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&minorsAge3=" + $("select[name='minorsAge3']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&minorsAge4=" + $("select[name='minorsAge4']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&departure_dt=" + $("select[name='departure_dt']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&arrival_dt=" + $("select[name='arrival_dt']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&departDateFlexibility=" + $("select[name='departDateFlexibility']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&returnDateFlexibility=" + $("select[name='returnDateFlexibility']", __cb).val();
                        return s;
                    },
                    compareAirports  : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("." + event.data.cb.options.currentView);
                        var _dt  = $(".cb-datetypes", __cb),
                            _bow = (event.data.cb.options.currentView == "form-fow");
                        var b520 = __cb.hasClass("cb520");
                        if ($(this).is(":checked")) {
                            $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).removeClass("cb-no-csa");
                            if (b520) {
                                $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).removeClass("span-2");
                                $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).addClass("span-3");
                            }
                            $(".cb-plus-minus", _dt).hide();
                            $(".cb-best-dates", _dt).hide();
                        } else {
                            $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).addClass("cb-no-csa");
                            if (b520) {
                                $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).removeClass("span-3");
                                $(".cb-exact-dates", _dt).addClass("span-2");
                            }
                            $(".cb-plus-minus", _dt).show();
                            $(".cb-best-dates", _dt).show();
                        }
                        if (_bow) {
                            $(".cb-plus-minus", _dt).hide();
                        }
                    },
                    dateType         : function (event) {
                        var __cb   = $("." + event.data.cb.options.currentView),
                            _v     = $(this).val(),
                            _m     = $(".cb-datetype-msg", __cb),
                            _csa   = $(".cb-csa input:checked", __cb),
                            _dates = $(".cal-group", __cb),
                            _bow   = (event.data.cb.options.currentView == "form-fow");
                        $("li", _m).hide();
                        _dates.removeClass("cb-exact-dates cb-plus-minus cb-best-dates");
                        switch (_v) {
                            case "exactDates":
                                $(".cb-csa", __cb).show();
                                $(".cb-date, .cb-exact-time", __cb).show();
                                $(".cb-flex-time,.cb-best-date", __cb).hide();
                                if ($(".cb-csa input:checked", __cb).length != 0) {
                                    $(".cb-exact-dates-msg", _m).show();
                                }
                                _dates.addClass("cb-exact-dates");
                                if (!_bow) {
                                    event
                                        .data
                                        .cb
                                        .flights
                                        .showFlightHotel(event.data.cb);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "plusMinusDates":
                                $(".cb-plus-minus-msg", _m).show();
                                $(".cb-date, .cb-flex-time", __cb).show();
                                $(".cb-exact-time,.cb-best-date", __cb).hide();
                                _dates.addClass("cb-plus-minus");
                                event
                                    .data
                                    .cb
                                    .flights
                                    .hideFlightHotel(event.data.cb);
                                break;
                            case "flexibleDates":
                                $(".cb-flex-dates-msg", _m).show();
                                $(".cb-csa", __cb).hide();
                                $(".cb-exact-time,.cb-date, .cb-flex-time", __cb).hide();
                                $(".cb-best-date", __cb).show();
                                _dates.addClass("cb-best-dates");
                                event
                                    .data
                                    .cb
                                    .flights
                                    .hideFlightHotel(event.data.cb);
                        }
                        if (_bow) {
                            var _rd = $(".cb-return-dates", __cb);
                            $(".cb-csa", __cb).hide();
                            $(".cb-date, .cb-flex-time,.cb-exact-time", _rd).hide();
                        }
                    },
                    hideFlightHotel  : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        if (cb.options.Service == "CJCA" || cb.options.Service == "TCYCA" || $(".cb-fh-submit-button", __cb).length == 0) {
                            return;
                        }
                        var b520 = cb
                            .options
                            .cb
                            .hasClass("cb520");
                        $(".cb-last-row", __cb).removeClass("cb-flight-submit");
                        if (b520) {
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).removeClass("span-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).addClass("cb-span-5");
                        } else {
                            $(".cb-submit-column", __cb).removeClass("span-5");
                            $(".cb-submit-column", __cb).addClass("span-3 prefix-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).removeClass("span-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).addClass("cb-span-3");
                        }
                        $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).html("Search Flights");
                        $(".cb-fh-submit-button,.cb-flight-submit-or", __cb).hide();
                        $(".cb-fh-submit-button", __cb).css("visibility", "hidden");
                    },
                    init             : function (cb) {
                        var _subnav,
                            __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        __cb.show();
                        cb.options.Service = $("input[name='Service']", cb.options.cb).val();
                        if (!cb.flights.ready) {
                            if ($(".cb-sub-nav", __cb).length != 0) {
                                _subnav = __cb.find(".cb-sub-nav input[name='subnav']");
                                for (var i = 0; i < _subnav.length; i += 1) {
                                    var nav = $(_subnav[i]);
                                    nav.bind("click", {
                                        cb: cb
                                    }, cb._changeView);
                                }
                            }
                            jQuery.extend(true, cb.options.datePicker, {
                                fromID  : "fo-fromdate",
                                maxRange: 26,
                                onError : cb.checkDates,
                                toID    : "fo-todate"
                            });
                            $(".cb-fromdate, .cb-todate", __cb).datepicker(cb.options.datePicker);
                            cb
                                .flights
                                .bindEvents(cb);
                            cb.flights.ready = true;
                        }
                        if ($(".cb-sub-nav", __cb).length != 0) {
                            _subnav                = __cb.find(".cb-sub-nav input[name='subnav']:checked");
                            cb.options.currentView = _subnav.val();
                        }
                        switch (cb.options.currentView) {
                            case "form-fow":
                                $(".cb-csa input", __cb).attr("checked", false);
                                $("input[name='flightType']", __cb).attr("value", "oneway");
                                if ($(".cb-datetypes input[value=plusMinusDates]", __cb).is(":checked")) {
                                    $(".cb-datetypes input[value=exactDates]", __cb).attr("checked", "checked");
                                }
                                __cb.addClass("form-fow");
                                cb
                                    .flights
                                    .hideFlightHotel(cb);
                                $("input[name='returningDate']", __cb).attr("value", cb.options.dateFormat);
                                break;
                            default:
                                $("input[name='flightType']", __cb).attr("value", "roundtrip");
                                __cb.removeClass("form-fow");
                        }
                        $(".cb-to-city,.cb-from-city,.cb-fromdate, .cb-todate,.cb-state,.cb-car-type,.cb-ch" +
                                "ildren,.cb-csa input,input[name='dateTypeSelect']:checked",
                        __cb).trigger("change");
                    },
                    multiDestSearch  : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        var s = "?Service=" + $("input[name='Service']", __cb).val();
                        s += event
                            .data
                            .cb
                            .flights
                            .collectForm(event);
                        s += "&leavingFrom=" + $("input[name='leavingFrom']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&leavingDate1=" + $("input[name='leavingDate']", __cb).val();
                        s += "&leavingTime1=" + $("select[name='dateLeavingTime']", __cb).val();
                        $(this).attr("href", $(this).attr("href") + s);
                    },
                    ready            : false,
                    searchFlightHotel: function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        var ca     = __cb.find(".cb-child-ages"),
                            a      = ca.find("select"),
                            _index = 0;
                        a.each(function (i) {
                            _index = i + 1;
                            $(this).attr("name", "minorAge" + _index + "Room1");
                        });
                        $("#cb-form-fo").attr("action", $("input[name='fhPath']", event.data.cb.options.cb).val());
                        $("#airTripType").removeAttr("disabled");
                        event.data.cb.options.flightXsell = true;
                    },
                    searchFlights    : function (event) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        var ca = __cb.find(".cb-child-ages"),
                            a  = ca.find("select");
                        a.each(function (i) {
                            $(this).attr("name", "minorsAge" + i);
                        });
                        $("#cb-form-fo").attr("action", $("input[name='foPath']", event.data.cb.options.cb).val());
                        document
                            .getElementById("airTripType")
                            .setAttribute("disabled", "disabled");
                        event.data.cb.options.flightXsell = false;
                    },
                    showChildAges    : function (event) {
                        var c  = $(this).val() - 1,
                            ca = $(this)
                                .parents("fieldset")
                                .find(".cb-child-ages"),
                            a  = ca.find("select");
                        (c == -1)
                            ? ca.hide()
                            : ca.show();
                        a.each(function (i) {
                            (c < i)
                                ? $(this).hide()
                                : $(this).show();
                        });
                    },
                    showFlightHotel  : function (cb) {
                        var __cb = $("#cb-form-fo");
                        if (cb.options.Service == "CJCA" || cb.options.Service == "TCYCA" || $(".cb-fh-submit-button", __cb).length == 0) {
                            return;
                        }
                        var b520 = cb
                            .options
                            .cb
                            .hasClass("cb520");
                        $(".cb-last-row", __cb).addClass("cb-flight-submit");
                        if (b520) {
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).addClass("span-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).removeClass("cb-span-5");
                        } else {
                            $(".cb-submit-column", __cb).addClass("span-5");
                            $(".cb-submit-column", __cb).removeClass("span-3 prefix-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).addClass("span-2");
                            $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).removeClass("cb-span-3");
                        }
                        $(".cb-flights-submit-button", __cb).html("Search<br />Flights");
                        $(".cb-fh-submit-button,.cb-flight-submit-or", __cb).show();
                        $(".cb-fh-submit-button", __cb).css("visibility", "visible");
                    }
                },
                gaTracking      : function (cb) {
                    var lob = (cb.split("-")[2])
                        ? cb.split("-")[2]
                        : cb.split("-")[1];
                    var from = jQuery("#" + lob + "-from").val();
                    var to = jQuery("#" + lob + "-to").val();
                    var fromDate = jQuery("#" + lob + "-fromdate").val();
                    var toDate = jQuery("#" + lob + "-todate").val();
                    var fromTime = jQuery("#" + lob + "-fromtime").val();
                    var toTime = jQuery("#" + lob + "-totime").val();
                    var totalRooms = jQuery("#" + lob + "-totalrooms").val();
                    var adults = jQuery("#" + lob + "-adult").val();
                    var children = jQuery("#" + lob + "-child").val();
                    var seniors = jQuery("#" + lob + "-seniors").val();
                    var paths = window
                        .location
                        .pathname
                        .split("/");
                    var trackingContext = "";
                    switch (paths[1]) {
                        case "Flights":
                            trackingContext = "AFD";
                            break;
                        case "Hotels":
                            trackingContext = "HFD";
                            break;
                        case "Vacations":
                            trackingContext = "PFD";
                            break;
                        case "Car-Rental":
                            trackingContext = "CFD";
                            break;
                        case "Cruises":
                            trackingContext = "UFD";
                            break;
                        default:
                            trackingContext = "HMP";
                            break;
                    }
                    switch (lob) {
                        case "fh":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Flight+Hotels", 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 7, "Origin", from, 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", to, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 10, "HowManyRms-Travelers", "rm" + totalRooms + "|Adult" + adults + "|Minor" + children + "|Senior" + seniors,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_trackEvent", trackingContext + ":CB",
                                "Search:Flights_only"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "fhc":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Flight+Hotel+Car", 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 7, "Origin", from, 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", to, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 10, "HowManyRms-Travelers", "rm" + totalRooms + "|Adult" + adults + "|Minor" + children + "|Senior" + seniors,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_trackEvent", trackingContext + "CB",
                                "Search:Flights+Hotel+Car"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "ho":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Hotel_only", 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", to, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);
                            var roomNo = jQuery("#ho-totalrooms").val();
                            var roomDetails = "";
                            for (var x = 1; x <= roomNo; x += 1) {
                                roomDetails += "rm" + x + "|" + jQuery("input#ho-adults" + x).val() + "|" + jQuery("input#ho-minors" + x).val();
                            }
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 11, "HowMany-Rms", roomDetails, 3]);
                            var topSecret = (jQuery("#ho-top-secret").val())
                                ? "FindTopSecret Hotel"
                                : "";
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 15, "CheckBox", topSecret, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_trackEvent", trackingContext + ":CB",
                                "Search:Hotel_only"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "hc":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Hotel+Car", 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", to, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);
                            var roomNo = jQuery("#hcx-totalrooms").val();
                            var roomDetails = "";
                            for (var x = 1; x <= roomNo; x += 1) {
                                roomDetails += "rm" + x + "|" + jQuery("input#hcx-adults" + x).val() + "|" + jQuery("input#hcx-minors" + x).val() + "|";
                            }
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 11, "HowMany-Rms", roomDetails, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_trackEvent", trackingContext + ":CB",
                                "Search:Hotel+Car"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "fo":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Flight_only", 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 7, "Origin", from, 3]);
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", to, 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 12, "HowMany-Flight_only", "Adult" + adults + "|Minor" + children + "|Senior" + seniors,
                                3
                            ]);
                            var tripType = jQuery("form#cb-form-fo input:radio[name='subnav']:checked").val();
                            var surroundingAirport = (jQuery("#fo-includeairport").attr("checked"))
                                ? "CompareSurroundingAirport"
                                : "";
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 15, "CheckBox", tripType + "|" + surroundingAirport,
                                3
                            ]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_trackEvent", trackingContext + ":CB",
                                "Search:Flights_only"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "co":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Car_only", 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 8, "Destination", jQuery("#co-pick-location").val() + "|" + to,
                                3
                            ]);

                                "_setCustomVar", 9, "Duration", fromDate + "|" + toDate + "|" + fromTime + "|" + toTime,
                                3
                            ]);

                                3
                            ]);

                                "Search:Car_only"
                            ]);
                            break;
                        case "cro":
                            _gaq.push(["_setCustomVar", 6, "SearchType", "Cruise", 3]);
                            _gaq.push([
                                "_setCustomVar", 8, to + "|" + jQuery("#cruiseLength").val() + "|" + jQuery("#cru-datemonth").val() + "|" + jQuery("#cro-cruiseline").val(),
                                3
                            ]);

                                ? "55yrs"
                                : "";

                                3
                            ]);

                                "Search:Cruise"
                            ]);
                            break;
                    }

            // *****END***** // The following js comes from:
            // http://i.travelpn.com/jquery/plug-ins/jquery.json2xml.min.js //
            (function ($) {
                $.json2xml = function (json, options) {
                    settings = {};
                    settings = $.extend(true, settings, defaultSettings, options || {});
                    return convertToXml(json, settings.rootTagName, "", 0);
                };
                var defaultSettings = {
                    exceptions     : [],
                    formatOutput   : false,
                    formatTextNodes: false,
                    ignore         : [],
                    indentString   : "  ",
                    nodes          : [],
                    replace        : [],
                    rootTagName    : "root"
                };
                var settings = {};
                var convertToXml = function (json, tagName, parentPath, depth) {
                    var suffix = (settings.formatOutput)
                        ? "\r\n"
                        : "";
                    var indent = (settings.formatOutput)
                        ? getIndent(depth)
                        : "";
                    var xmlTag = indent + "<" + tagName;
                    var children = "";
                    for (var key in json) {
                        if (json.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
                            var propertyPath = parentPath + key;
                            var propertyName = getPropertyName(parentPath, key);
                            if ($.inArray(propertyPath, settings.ignore) == -1) {
                                if ($.isArray(json[key])) {
                                    children += createNodeFromArray(json[key], propertyName, propertyPath + ".", depth + 1, suffix);
                                } else if (typeof(json[key]) === "object") {
                                    children += convertToXml(json[key], propertyName, propertyPath + ".", depth + 1);
                                } else {
                                    if ($.inArray(propertyPath, settings.nodes) != -1) {
                                        children += createTextNode(propertyName, json[key], depth, suffix);
                                    } else {
                                        xmlTag += " " + propertyName + "='" + json[key] + "'";
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    if (children !== "") {
                        xmlTag += ">" + suffix + children + indent + "</" + tagName + ">" + suffix;
                    } else {
                        xmlTag += "/>" + suffix;
                    }
                    return xmlTag;
                };
                var getIndent = function (depth) {
                    var output = "";
                    for (var i = 0; i < depth; i += 1) {
                        output += settings.indentString;
                    }
                    return output;
                };
                var getPropertyName = function (parentPath, name) {
                    var index = settings.replace.length;
                    var searchName = parentPath + name;
                    while (index--) {
                        if (settings.replace[index].hasOwnProperty(searchName)) {
                            return settings.replace[index][searchName];
                        }
                    }
                    return name;
                };
                var createNodeFromArray = function (source, name, path, depth, suffix) {
                    var xmlNode = "";
                    if (source.length > 0) {
                        for (var index in source) {
                            if (typeof(source[index]) !== "object") {
                                if (source[index] === "") {
                                    xmlNode += getIndent(depth) + "<" + name + "/>" + suffix;
                                } else {
                                    var textPrefix = (settings.formatTextNodes)
                                        ? suffix + getIndent(depth + 1)
                                        : "";
                                    var textSuffix = (settings.formatTextNodes)
                                        ? suffix + getIndent(depth)
                                        : "";
                                    xmlNode += getIndent(depth) + "<" + name + ">" + textPrefix + source[index] + textSuffix + "</" + name + ">" + suffix;
                                }
                            } else {
                                xmlNode += convertToXml(source[index], name, path, depth);
                            }
                        }
                    } else {
                        xmlNode += getIndent(depth) + "<" + name + "/>" + suffix;
                    }
                    return xmlNode;
                };
                var createTextNode = function (name, text, parentDepth, suffix) {
                    var textPrefix = (settings.formatTextNodes)
                        ? suffix + getIndent(parentDepth + 2)
                        : "";
                    var textSuffix = (settings.formatTextNodes)
                        ? suffix + getIndent(parentDepth + 1)
                        : "";
                    var xmlNode = getIndent(parentDepth + 1) + "<" + name + ">" + textPrefix + text + textSuffix + "</" + name + ">" + suffix;
                    return xmlNode;
                };
            })(jQuery); // .
            // *****END***** // The following js comes from:
            // http://i.travelpn.com/js/subscription_management.js //
            (function () {
                jQuery(function () {
                    SubscriptionsConstants = {
                        COMUNICATION_ERROR_RESPONSE   : "communication_error",
                        DASHING_DEALS_SOURCE          : 44,
                        DEFAULT_SERVICE               : "TRAVELOCITY",
                        EXISTING_ACCOUNT_RESPONSE     : "existing_account",
                        FAILURE_RESPONSE              : "failure",
                        HOMEPAGE_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE  : 1,
                        INVALID_PARAMETERS_RESPONSE   : "invalid_parameters",
                        LINK_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE      : 4,
                        MAX_RETRIES                   : -1,
                        MISSING_PARAMETERS_RESPONSE   : "missing_required_parameters",
                        MULTI_MATCH_RESPONSE          : "multi_match",
                        NEW_ACCOUNT_RESPONSE          : "new_account",
                        NO_MATCH_RESPONSE             : "no_match",
                        REGISTER_REQUEST              : "register",
                        SINGLE_MATCH_RESPONSE         : "single_match",
                        STANDALONE_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE: 2,
                        SUBSCRIBRE_REQUEST            : "subscribe",
                        SUCCESS_RESPONSE              : "success",
                        VS_TRACK_CODES                : {
                            COMUNICATION_ERROR_RESPONSE: "CommunicationError",
                            EXISTING_ACCOUNT           : "ExistingAccount",
                            INVALID_PARAMETERS         : "InvalidParameters",
                            MISSING_PARAMETERS         : "MissingParameters",
                            MULTI_MATCH                : "MultiMatch",
                            NEW_ACCOUNT                : "NewAccount",
                            NO_MATCH                   : "NoMatch",
                            SINGLE_MATCH               : "SingleMatch",
                            TRACKING_PREFIX            : "Subscriptions"
                        }
                    };
                    if (typeof(Subscriptions) !== "object") {
                        Subscriptions = {};
                    }
                    jQuery.extend(Subscriptions, SubscriptionsConstants);
                });
                if (typeof(Subscriptions) !== "object") {
                    Subscriptions = {};
                }
            })();
            Subscriptions.Signup                            = (function () {
                var popup;
                var signup_module;
