                var module_states = {
                    HP_WIDGET  : "HomePageWidget",
                    SA_WIDGET  : "Widget",
                    SIGNUP     : "SignUp",
                    SIGNUP_LINK: "SignUpLink"
                };
                function _Popup() {
                    var Popup = function () {};
                    Popup.prototype = {
                        hideWindow: function () {
                            if (popup.win) {
                                popup
                                    .win
                                    .close();
                            }
                        },
                        iPopupH   : 0,
                        iPopupW   : 0,
                        oUrls     : {},
                        setUp     : function (popup_config) {
                            this.iPopupH                 = popup_config.height
                                ? popup_config.height
                                : 400;
                            this.iPopupW                 = popup_config.width
                                ? popup_config.width
                                : 500;
                            this.win2.winfeatures.width  = this.iPopupW;
                            this.win2.winfeatures.height = this.iPopupH;
                            this.oUrls                   = popup_config.urls
                                ? popup_config.urls
                                : {};
                        },
                        show      : function () {
                            var sPopupState = arguments[0];
                            var sUrlArgs = arguments[1];
                            var sPopupUrl = "";
                            var sstate = arguments[4] == module_states.SIGNUP_LINK
                                ? module_states.SIGNUP_LINK
                                : module_states.SIGNUP;
                            switch (sPopupState) {
                                case "SignUpPopup":
                                    sPopupUrl = this.oUrls.SignUpPopup;
                                    break;
                            }
                            if (sPopupUrl !== "") {
                                if (popup.win) {
                                    var winBody = popup
                                        .win
                                        .document
                                        .getElementsByTagName("body")[0];
                                    if (winBody) {
                                        var subscription_form = popup
                                            .win
                                            .document
                                            .createElement("form");
                                        subscription_form.method = "POST";
                                        subscription_form.action = sPopupUrl;
                                        var subscription_state = popup
                                            .win
                                            .document
                                            .createElement("input");
                                        subscription_state.type  = "hidden";
                                        subscription_state.name  = "State";
                                        subscription_state.value = sstate;
                                        subscription_form.appendChild(subscription_state);
                                        var subscription_email = popup
                                            .win
                                            .document
                                            .createElement("input");
                                        subscription_email.type  = "hidden";
                                        subscription_email.name  = "Email";
                                        subscription_email.value = arguments[1];
                                        subscription_form.appendChild(subscription_email);
                                        var subscription_source = popup
                                            .win
                                            .document
                                            .createElement("input");
                                        subscription_source.type  = "hidden";
                                        subscription_source.name  = "subscriptionsource";
                                        subscription_source.value = arguments[2];
                                        subscription_form.appendChild(subscription_source);
                                        var subscription_servicetag = popup
                                            .win
                                            .document
                                            .createElement("input");
                                        subscription_servicetag.type  = "hidden";
                                        subscription_servicetag.name  = "Service";
                                        subscription_servicetag.value = arguments[3];
                                        subscription_form.appendChild(subscription_servicetag);
                                        winBody.appendChild(subscription_form);
                                        subscription_form.submit();
                                    }
                                    popup
                                        .win
                                        .focus();
                                    window.blur();
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        showWindow: function () {
                            this
                                .win2
                                .init(popup.win2.winfeatures);
                        },
                        win       : null,
                        win2      : {
                            init       : function (winfeatures) {
                                winfeatures.left = (screen.width / 2) - (winfeatures.width / 2);
                                winfeatures.top  = (screen.height / 2) - (winfeatures.height / 2);
                                var windowfeautres = (function (features_object) {
                                    var features = [];
                                    for (feature in features_object) {
                                        features.push(feature + "=" + features_object[feature]);
                                    }
                                    return features.join(",");
                                })(winfeatures);
                                popup.win = window.open("", "RegistrationWindow" + (new Date()).getTime(), windowfeautres);
                                popup
                                    .win
                                    .blur();
                                popup.win.screenX = (screen.width / 2) - (winfeatures.width / 2);
                                popup.win.screenY = (screen.height / 2) - (winfeatures.height / 2);
                            },
                            winfeatures: {
                                directories: "0",
                                height     : "400",
                                left       : "150",
                                location   : "0",
                                menubar    : "0",
                                resizable  : "0",
                                scrollbars : "0",
                                status     : "1",
                                toolbar    : "0",
                                top        : "200",
                                width      : "500"
                            }
                        }
                    };
                    return new Popup();
                }
                function _SignupModule(module_instance) {
                    var module = function () {};
                    module.prototype = {
                        collectFormData         : function () {
                            var data = {};
                            jQuery(":input", document.forms[this.oForm.name]).each(function (e, ix) {
                                var $this = jQuery(this);
                                data[$this.attr("name")] = jQuery.trim($this.attr("value"));
                            });
                            return data;
                        },
                        displayMsg              : function () {
                            var msg = arguments[1];
                            var type = arguments[0];
                            jQuery("#" + type).html(msg);
                            for (var i = 2; i < arguments.length; i += 1) {
                                jQuery("#" + arguments[i]).show();
                            }
                        },
                        emptyWidgetFields       : function () {
                            var oScope = this;
                            switch (this.sState) {
                                case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    break;
                                case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    for (var e = 0; e < oScope.oForm.elements.length; e += 1) {
                                        if (oScope.oForm.elements[e].name != "submit") {
                                            oScope.oForm.elements[e].value = "";
                                        }
                                    }
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    for (var e = 0; e < oScope.oForm.elements.length; e += 1) {
                                        if (oScope.oForm.elements[e].tagName != "BUTTON") {
                                            oScope.oForm.elements[e].value = "";
                                        }
                                    }
                                    break;
                            }
                        },
                        fServiceResponseCallback: function (msgStatus, formData, serviceResponse) {
                            return true;
                        },
                        hide                    : function () {
                            var to_hide = [];
                            for (var h = 0; h < arguments.length; h += 1) {
                                var e = $(arguments[h]);
                                if (e !== null) {
                                    to_hide.push("#" + arguments[h]);
                                }
                            }
                            try {
                                jQuery(to_hide.join(",")).hide();
                            } catch (e) {}
                        },
                        iRetries                : 0,
                        iSbsSource              : 1,
                        oEventListeners         : {
                            onCollectSubscription      : function () {
                                this.oFormData = this.collectFormData();
                                jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataCollected");
                            },
                            onDataCollected            : function () {},
                            onDataNotValid             : function () {
                                var field_error = arguments[0];
                                var oe = jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sErrorMessagesModule).get(0);
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeImage, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText);
                                        if (field_error === this.oValidationErrorCodes.sBadMail) {
                                            this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail);
                                            this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        } else {
                                            this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail);
                                            this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        }
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeImage, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText, this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        if (field_error === this.oValidationErrorCodes.sBadMail) {
                                            this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail);
                                            this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        } else {
                                            this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail);
                                            this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        }
                                        switch (field_error) {
                                            case this.oValidationErrorCodes.sBadMail:
                                                jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule).addClass("bad-mail");
                                                jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail).show();
                                                break;
                                            case this.oValidationErrorCodes.sLongMail:
                                                jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule).addClass("long-mail");
                                                break;
                                        }
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule);
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sMultiMatchModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule);
                                        if (field_error === this.oValidationErrorCodes.sSignupError) {
                                            this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleAutoMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule);
                                            this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail);
                                            this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, oe[field_error].value);
                                            this.iRetries += 1;
                                        } else {
                                            if (field_error === this.oValidationErrorCodes.sBadMail) {
                                                this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, oe.e_msg_badmail.value);
                                                this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, oe.e_detail_badmail.value);
                                            } else {
                                                this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, oe.e_msg_invalid_information.value);
                                                this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, oe.e_msg_to_do.value + oe[field_error].value);
                                            }
                                        }
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onDataValid                : function () {
                                this.setState();
                                jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataCollect");
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeImage);
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText);
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleLongMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError, this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onDataValidate             : function () {
                                var oScope = this;
                                if (this.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET) {
                                    jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule).removeClass("try-again long-mail bad-mail");
                                    jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail).hide();
                                }
                                var errors = this.validateFormData();
                                if (errors.length > 0) {
                                    jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataNotValid", errors);
                                } else {
                                    jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataValid");
                                }
                            },
                            onExistingAccount          : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule);
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sNoMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule);
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sNoMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onInvalidParameters        : function () {
                                jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataValidate");
                            },
                            onMaxRetries               : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail).attr("disabled", "disabled");
                                        jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMailConfirm).attr("disabled", "disabled");
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onMissingRequiredParameters: function () {
                                jQuery(this.oForm).trigger("eDataValidate");
                            },
                            onMultiMatch               : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule, this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule);
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        $(this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModuleMail).innerHTML = this.oFormData.Email + ".<br><br>";
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule, this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModuleMail, this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModuleMailLabel);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onNewAccount               : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        $(this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModuleMail).innerHTML = this.oFormData.Email + ".<br><br>";
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModule);
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onNoMatch                  : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule, this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sMultiMatchModule);
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sNoMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        popup.show("SignUpPopup", this.oFormData.Email, this.iSbsSource, this.sService);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        popup.show("SignUpPopup", this.oFormData.Email, this.iSbsSource, this.sService);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onResponse                 : function () {
                                this.responseBack = 1;
                            },
                            onSingleMatch              : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule);
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        $(this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModuleMail).innerHTML = this.oFormData.Email;
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onSubscriptionFailure      : function () {
                                switch (this.sState) {
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText);
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeImage, this.oWidgetComponents.sLongMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                        jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule).addClass("try-again");
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeImage, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeText, this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleComError);
                                        this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleBadMail, this.oWidgetComponents.sLongMail);
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        var oe = $(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorMessagesModule);
                                        this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule);
                                        this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sMultiMatchModule, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule);
                                        this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, oe[this.oValidationErrorCodes.sComunicationError].value);
                                        break;
                                }
                            },
                            onSubscriptionFinished     : function () {}
                        },
                        oEvents                 : {
                            eDataCollect         : null,
                            eDataCollected       : null,
                            eDataNotValid        : null,
                            eDataValid           : null,
                            eDataValidate        : null,
                            eSubscriptionFinished: null
                        },
                        oForm                   : null,
                        oFormData               : null,
                        oPopupComponents        : {
                            sAgreementTerms           : "terms-and-conditions",
                            sAlertModule              : "alert-msg",
                            sCloseWindowControl       : "popup-component-close",
                            sErrorDetailsModule       : "error-details",
                            sErrorMessagesModule      : "popup-error-codes",
                            sErrorModule              : "error-msg",
                            sExistingAccountModule    : "popup-existing-account",
                            sGoodMail                 : "good-mail-logo",
                            sIntroTextModule          : "intro-txt",
                            sMultiMatchModule         : "popup-registered-account",
                            sNewAccountModule         : "popup-registered-account",
                            sNewAccountModuleMail     : "sub-mgmt-ty-mail",
                            sNewAccountModuleMailLabel: "sub-mgmt-ty-mail-label",
                            sNoMatchModule            : "popup-no-account",
                            sPrintControl             : "popup-component-print",
                            sSignupModule             : "popup-register-account",
                            sSignupModuleAutoMail     : "auto-email",
                            sSignupModuleForm         : "email-submit",
                            sSignupModuleLastName     : "signup-lname",
                            sSignupModuleMail         : "signup-email",
                            sSignupModuleMailConfirm  : "signup-email-confirm",
                            sSignupModuleName         : "signup-fname",
                            sSignupModuleSubmit       : "email-signup-submit",
                            sSignupModuleZipCode      : "signup-zip",
                            sSingleMatchModule        : ""
                        },
                        oSubscriptionEvents     : {
                            ExistingAccount          : null,
                            InvalidParameters        : null,
                            MaxRetries               : null,
                            MissingRequiredParameters: null,
                            MultiMatch               : null,
                            NewAccount               : null,
                            NoMatch                  : null,
                            Response                 : null,
                            SingleMatch              : null,
                            SubscriptionFailure      : null
                        },
                        oValidationErrorCodes   : {
                            sBadMail          : "e_detail_badmail",
                            sComunicationError: "e_msg_comunication",
                            sEmptyFirstName   : "e_msg_fname_not_filled",
                            sEmptyLastName    : "e_msg_lname_not_filled",
                            sEmptyZip         : "e_msg_zip_not_filled",
                            sInvalidFirstName : "e_msg_fname_invalid",
                            sInvalidLastName  : "e_msg_lname_invalid",
                            sInvalidZip       : "e_msg_zip_invalid",
                            sLongFirstName    : "e_msg_fname_length",
                            sLongLastName     : "e_msg_lname_length",
                            sLongMail         : "e_msg_mail_length",
                            sSignupError      : "e_msg_signup_error"
                        },
                        oWidgetComponents       : {
                            sExistingAccountModule     : "sm-div-existing-account",
                            sMultiMatchModule          : "widget-subscribed-account",
                            sNoMatchModule             : "sm-div-verify",
                            sSignupModule              : "widget-subscribe-account",
                            sSignupModuleBadMail       : "sm-div-verify",
                            sSignupModuleComError      : "sm-div-verify",
                            sSignupModuleForm          : "hp-email-submit",
                            sSignupModuleLongMail      : "sm-div-verify",
                            sSignupModuleSubmit        : "hp-submit",
                            sSignupModuleSubscribeImage: "subscribe-image",
                            sSignupModuleSubscribeMail : "hp-subscribe-email",
                            sSignupModuleSubscribeText : "sm-signup",
                            sSingleMatchModule         : "widget-subscribed-account"
                        },
                        responseBack            : -1,
                        setState                : function () {
                            if (typeof arguments[0] == "string") {
                                this.sState = arguments[0];
                            }
                            var oe = jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sErrorMessagesModule).get(0);
                            switch (this.sState) {
                                case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                    this.displayMsg(this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule, oe.i_txt_signup.value);
                                    this.hide(this.oPopupComponents.sMultiMatchModule, this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sNewAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sExistingAccountModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorModule, this.oPopupComponents.sErrorDetailsModule, this.oPopupComponents.sAlertModule);
                                    this.show(this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModule, this.oPopupComponents.sGoodMail, this.oPopupComponents.sIntroTextModule);
                                    break;
                                case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                    this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule);
                                    this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule, this.oWidgetComponents.sNoMatchModule, this.oWidgetComponents.sExistingAccountModule);
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                    this.show(this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModule);
                                    this.hide(this.oWidgetComponents.sSingleMatchModule, this.oWidgetComponents.sNoMatchModule);
                                    break;
                            }
                        },
                        setUp                   : function (module_config) {
                            var oScope = this;
                            String.prototype.trim = function () {
                                return this
                                    .replace(/^\s*/, "")
                                    .replace(/\s*$/, "");
                            };
                            if (typeof(module_config.oWidgetComponents) == "object") {
                                for (comp in module_config.oWidgetComponents) {
                                    if (typeof(oScope.oWidgetComponents[comp]) !== "undefined") {
                                        oScope.oWidgetComponents[comp] = module_config.oWidgetComponents[comp];
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            if (typeof(module_config.fServiceResponseCallback) == "function") {
                                oScope.fServiceResponseCallback = module_config.fServiceResponseCallback;
                            }
                            if (typeof(module_config.oPopupComponents) == "object") {
                                for (comp in module_config.oPopupComponents) {
                                    if (typeof(oScope.oPopupComponents[comp]) !== "undefined") {
                                        oScope.oPopupComponents[comp] = module_config.oPopupComponents[comp];
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            var signup_module = this;
                            oScope.sState     = module_config.state
                                ? module_config.state
                                : "Widget";
                            oScope.iSbsSource = module_config.subscriptionsource
                                ? module_config.subscriptionsource
                                : Subscriptions.HOMEPAGE_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE;
                            oScope.sService   = module_config.servicetag && module_config.servicetag !== ""
                                ? module_config.servicetag
                                : Subscriptions.DEFAULT_SERVICE;
                            if (oScope.iSbsSource == Subscriptions.LINK_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE && oScope.sState == module_states.SIGNUP_LINK) {
                                jQuery(module_config.subscription_link)
                                    .bind("click", function (e) {
                                        e.preventDefault();
                                        popup.showWindow();
                                        popup.show("SignUpPopup", "", oScope.iSbsSource, oScope.sService, module_states.SIGNUP);
                                    });
                                if (oScope.sState !== module_states.SIGNUP) {
                                    return;
                                }
                            }
                            switch (oScope.sState) {
                                case module_states.SIGNUP_LINK:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    break;
                                case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    for (var e = 0; e < oScope.oForm.elements.length; e += 1) {
                                        if (oScope.oForm.elements[e].name != "submit") {
                                            this.oForm.elements[e].value = "";
                                        }
                                    }
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                    oScope.oForm = jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleForm).get(0);
                                    for (var e = 0; e < oScope.oForm.elements.length; e += 1) {
                                        if (oScope.oForm.elements[e].tagName != "BUTTON") {
                                            this.oForm.elements[e].value = "";
                                        }
                                    }
                                    break;
                            }
                            oScope.emptyWidgetFields();
                            for (evt in oScope.oSubscriptionEvents) {
                                jQuery(oScope.oForm)
                                    .bind(evt, oScope, function (e) {
                                        e
                                            .data
                                            .oEventListeners["on" + e.type]
                                            .apply(e.data);
                                    });
                            }
                            if (oScope.iSbsSource == Subscriptions.DASHING_DEALS_SOURCE) {
                                for (evt in oScope.oSubscriptionEvents) {
                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm)
                                        .bind("Track" + evt, {
                                            evttype: evt,
                                            scope  : oScope
                                        }, function (e) {
                                            if (typeof(_gaq) == "object") {
                                                switch (e.data.evttype) {
                                                    case "NoMatch":
                                                        _gaq.push(["_trackEvent", "DoD", "NL Signup Start", "DoD page"]);
                                                        break;
                                                    case "NewAccount":
                                                        _gaq.push(["_trackEvent", "DoD", "DoD:NL Signup Submit", "new user"]);
                                                        break;
                                                    case "ExistingAccount":
                                                    case "SingleMatch":
                                                    case "MultiMatch":
                                                        _gaq.push(["_trackEvent", "DoD", "DoD:NL Signup Submit", "existing user"]);
                                                        break;
                                                }
                                            }
                                        });
                                }
                            }
                            jQuery(oScope.oForm)
                                .bind("eDataCollect", oScope, function (e) {
                                    e
                                        .data
                                        .oEventListeners
                                        .onCollectSubscription
                                        .apply(e.data);
                                });
                            jQuery(oScope.oForm).bind("eDataCollected", oScope, function (e) {
                                e
                                    .data
                                    .oEventListeners
                                    .onDataCollected
                                    .apply(e.data);
                            });
                            jQuery(this.oForm).bind("eDataValidate", oScope, function (e) {
                                e
                                    .data
                                    .oEventListeners
                                    .onDataValidate
                                    .apply(e.data);
                            });
                            jQuery(this.oForm).bind("eDataValid", oScope, function (e) {
                                e
                                    .data
                                    .oEventListeners
                                    .onDataValid
                                    .apply(e.data);
                            });
                            jQuery(this.oForm).bind("eDataNotValid", oScope, function (e, errors) {
                                e
                                    .data
                                    .oEventListeners
                                    .onDataNotValid
                                    .apply(e.data, [errors]);
                            });
                            var emailSubmit = false;
                            var emailField = false;
                            switch (this.sState) {
                                case module_states.SIGNUP_LINK:
                                    emailSubmit = this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleSubmit;
                                    jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleAutoMail).html(jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail).attr("value"));
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                    emailSubmit = this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleSubmit;
                                    jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleAutoMail).html(jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail).attr("value"));
                                    break;
                                case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                    emailSubmit = this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubmit;
                                    emailField  = this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail;
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                    emailSubmit = this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubmit;
                                    emailField  = this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail;
                                    break;
                            }
                            var onSubmit = function (e) {
                                if ((oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET || oScope.sState == module_states.SA_WIDGET) && !(jQuery("#" + oScope.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail).attr("value").match(/[A-Za-z0-9._+\-]+/))) {
                                    return;
                                }
                                jQuery(e.data.oForm).trigger("eDataValidate");
                                var oRequestMode = "";
                                switch (oScope.sState) {
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP_LINK:
                                        oRequestMode = Subscriptions.REGISTER_REQUEST;
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                        oRequestMode = Subscriptions.REGISTER_REQUEST;
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                        oRequestMode = Subscriptions.SUBSCRIBRE_REQUEST;
                                        break;
                                    case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                        oRequestMode = Subscriptions.SUBSCRIBRE_REQUEST;
                                        break;
                                }
                                var oServiceResponse = "";
                                var oRequestConfig = {
                                    MaxRetries : module_config.maxRetries,
                                    oScope     : signup_module,
                                    sJSID      : module_config.JSID,
                                    sSID       : module_config.SID,
                                    sVSTrackUrl: module_config.sVSTrackUrl,
                                    XHRsrc     : module_config.serviceUrl
                                };
                                var oSubscriptionRequest = {
                                    cache          : false,
                                    iMaxRetries    : 0,
                                    iRetries       : 0,
                                    oResponseSchema: {
                                        fields    : [
                                            "Status", "Message"
                                        ],
                                        resultNode: "SubscriptionResponse"
                                    },
                                    sendRequest    : function (sXHRXmlReq, callback) {
                                        if (oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET) {
                                            jQuery("#" + emailSubmit).addClass("display_inactive");
                                        }
                                        jQuery.ajaxSetup({
                                            async      : false,
                                            beforeSend : function (xhr) {
                                                xhr.setRequestHeader(oSubscriptionRequest.sJSIDKey, oSubscriptionRequest.sJSID);
                                                xhr.setRequestHeader(oSubscriptionRequest.sSIDKey, oSubscriptionRequest.sSID);
                                                return true;
                                            },
                                            cache      : false,
                                            contentType: "text/xml",
                                            dataType   : "xml",
                                            error      : callback.failure,
                                            processData: false,
                                            success    : callback.success,
                                            timeout    : oSubscriptionRequest.timeout,
                                            type       : "POST",
                                            url        : oSubscriptionRequest.XHRsrc
                                        });
                                        jQuery.ajax({data: sXHRXmlReq});
                                    },
                                    setUp          : function (oRequestConfig) {
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.XHRsrc) == "string") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.XHRsrc = oRequestConfig.XHRsrc;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.sJSID) == "string") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.sJSID = oRequestConfig.sJSID;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.sSID) == "string") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.sSID = oRequestConfig.sSID;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.oResponseSchema) == "object") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.oResponseSchema = oRequestConfig.oResponseSchema;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.timeout) == "number") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.timeout = oRequestConfig.timeout;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.sVSTrackUrl) == "string") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl = oRequestConfig.sVSTrackUrl;
                                        }
                                        if (typeof(oRequestConfig.iMaxRetries) == "number") {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.iMaxRetries = oRequestConfig.MaxRetries;
                                        } else {
                                            oSubscriptionRequest.iMaxRetries = Subscriptions.MAX_RETRIES;
                                        }
                                    },
                                    sJSID          : "",
                                    sJSIDKey       : "OTHER_ID",
                                    sSID           : "",
                                    sSIDKey        : "SESSION_ID",
                                    sVSTrackUrl    : "",
                                    timeout        : 10000,
                                    XHRsrc         : ""
                                };
                                var oSubscriptionCallback = {
                                    failure: function (o) {
                                        if (oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET) {
                                            jQuery("#" + emailSubmit).removeClass("display_inactive");
                                        }
                                        var continueProcessing = oScope.fServiceResponseCallback(SubscriptionsConstants.FAILURE_RESPONSE, oScope.oFormData, "");
                                        if (continueProcessing) {
                                            jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("SubscriptionFailure");
                                        }
                                    },
                                    success: function (xml) {
                                        var oSubscriptionResponse = {};
                                        if (oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET) {
                                            jQuery("#" + emailSubmit).removeClass("display_inactive");
                                        }
                                        jQuery(xml)
                                            .find(oSubscriptionRequest.oResponseSchema.resultNode)
                                            .each(function () {
                                                oSubscriptionResponse.Status  = jQuery(this)
                                                    .find("Status")
                                                    .text();
                                                oSubscriptionResponse.Message = jQuery(this)
                                                    .find("Message")
                                                    .text();
                                                oServiceResponse              = oSubscriptionResponse.Message;
                                            });
                                        var continueProcessing = oScope.fServiceResponseCallback(oSubscriptionResponse.Status, oScope.oFormData, xml);
                                        if (!continueProcessing) {
                                            return;
                                        }
                                        if (oSubscriptionResponse.Status == Subscriptions.SUCCESS_RESPONSE) {
                                            switch (oSubscriptionResponse.Message) {
                                                case Subscriptions.SINGLE_MATCH_RESPONSE:
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("TrackSingleMatch");
                                                    vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.SINGLE_MATCH);
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("SingleMatch");
                                                    break;
                                                case Subscriptions.MULTI_MATCH_RESPONSE:
                                                    vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.MULTI_MATCH);
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("TrackMultiMatch");
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("MultiMatch");
                                                    break;
                                                case Subscriptions.NEW_ACCOUNT_RESPONSE:
                                                    vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.NEW_ACCOUNT);
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("TrackNewAccount");
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("NewAccount");
                                                    break;
                                                case Subscriptions.EXISTING_ACCOUNT_RESPONSE:
                                                    vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.EXISTING_ACCOUNT);
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("TrackExistingAccount");
                                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("ExistingAccount");
                                                    break;
                                            }
                                        } else {
                                            if (oSubscriptionResponse.Status == Subscriptions.FAILURE_RESPONSE) {
                                                switch (oSubscriptionResponse.Message) {
                                                    case Subscriptions.INVALID_PARAMETERS_RESPONSE:
                                                        vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.INVALID_PARAMETERS);
                                                        jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("InvalidParameters");
                                                        break;
                                                    case Subscriptions.MISSING_PARAMETERS_RESPONSE:
                                                        vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.MISSING_PARAMETERS);
                                                        jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("MissingRequiredParameters");
                                                        break;
                                                    case Subscriptions.COMUNICATION_ERROR_RESPONSE:
                                                        vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.COMUNICATION_ERROR_RESPONSE);
                                                        jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("SubscriptionFailure");
                                                        break;
                                                    case Subscriptions.EXISTING_ACCOUNT_RESPONSE:
                                                        vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.EXISTING_ACCOUNT);
                                                        jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("ExistingAccount");
                                                        break;
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                };
                                if ((oScope.validateFormData()).length == 0 && oScope.oFormData) {
                                    var sData = oScope.uGetXMLRequest(oRequestMode, oScope.oFormData, oScope.iRetries, oScope.iSbsSource);
                                    oSubscriptionRequest.setUp(oRequestConfig);
                                    oSubscriptionRequest.sendRequest(sData, oSubscriptionCallback);
                                }
                                if (oServiceResponse == Subscriptions.NO_MATCH_RESPONSE && (oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET || oScope.sState == module_states.SA_WIDGET)) {
                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("TrackNoMatch");
                                    popup.showWindow();
                                    jQuery(oScope.oForm).trigger("NoMatch");
                                    vsTrackClick(oSubscriptionRequest.sVSTrackUrl, Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.TRACKING_PREFIX + "." + oScope.sState + "." + Subscriptions.VS_TRACK_CODES.NO_MATCH);
                                    oScope.emptyWidgetFields();
                                }
                                return false;
                            };
                            if (emailField) {
                                jQuery("#" + this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail)
                                    .bind("keyup", oScope, function (e) {
                                        if (e.keyCode == 13) {
                                            onSubmit(e);
                                        }
                                    });
                            }
                            jQuery("#" + emailSubmit)
                                .bind("click", oScope, function (e) {
                                    onSubmit(e);
                                });
                            if (oScope.sState == module_states.HP_WIDGET) {
                                jQuery("#" + emailSubmit)
                                    .hover(function () {
                                        jQuery(this).addClass("hover");
                                    }, function () {
                                        jQuery(this).removeClass("hover");
                                    });
                            }
                            if (this.sState === "SignUp") {
                                jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sPrintControl)
                                    .bind("click", function (e) {
                                        window.print();
                                    });
                                jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sCloseWindowControl).bind("click", function (e) {
                                    window.close();
                                });
                                if (module_config.terms_link.url) {
                                    jQuery("#" + this.oPopupComponents.sAgreementTerms)
                                        .bind("click", function (e) {
                                            (function (url, features_object) {
                                                var features = [];
                                                for (feature in features_object) {
                                                    features.push(feature + "=" + features_object[feature]);
                                                }
                                                var terms_window_attr = features.join(",");
                                                var win = window.open(url, "TermsAndConditions", terms_window_attr);
                                                win.focus();
                                                win.screenX = 0;
                                                win.screenY = 0;
                                            })(module_config.terms_link.url, {
                                                directories: "0",
                                                height     : module_config.terms_link.height,
                                                left       : "0",
                                                location   : "0",
                                                menubar    : "0",
                                                resizable  : "0",
                                                scrollbars : "1",
                                                status     : "1",
                                                toolbar    : "0",
                                                top        : "0",
                                                width      : module_config.terms_link.width
                                            });
                                        });
                                }
                            }
                            this.setState();
                        },
                        show                    : function () {
                            var to_show = [];
                            for (var s = 0; s < arguments.length; s += 1) {
                                var e = $(arguments[s]);
                                if (e !== null) {
                                    to_show.push("#" + arguments[s]);
                                }
                            }
                            try {
                                jQuery(to_show.join(",")).show();
                            } catch (e) {}
                        },
                        sService                : "",
                        sState                  : "",
                        uGetXMLRequest          : function () {
                            var sXmlRequest = "";
                            sXmlRequest += "<Action>" + arguments[0] + "</Action>";
                            for (element in arguments[1]) {
                                switch (element) {
                                    case "Email":
                                        sXmlRequest += "<Email>" + arguments[1][element] + "</Email>";
                                        break;
                                    case "FirstName":
                                        sXmlRequest += "<FirstName>" + arguments[1][element] + "</FirstName>";
                                        break;
                                    case "LastName":
                                        sXmlRequest += "<LastName>" + arguments[1][element] + "</LastName>";
                                        break;
                                    case "Zip":
                                        sXmlRequest += "<Zip>" + arguments[1][element] + "</Zip>";
                                        break;
                                }
                            }
                            sXmlRequest += "<SubscriptionSource>" + arguments[3] + "</SubscriptionSource>";
                            if (arguments[2] >= 1) {
                                sXmlRequest += "<Retry>" + arguments[2] + "</Retry>";
                            } else {
                                if (("" + arguments[3]) == Subscriptions.LINK_SUBSCRIPTION_SOURCE) {
                                    sXmlRequest += "<Retry>1</Retry>";
                                }
                            }
                            sXmlRequest = "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><SubscriptionRequest xsi:noNamespaceSchema" +
                                    "Location='subMgmt.xsd' xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance'>" + sXmlRequest + "</SubscriptionRequest>";
                            return sXmlRequest;
                        },
                        validateFormData        : function () {
                            var oScope = this;
                            valid = true;
                            var errors = [];
                            var validate = {
                                Email            : function (mail) {
                                    var mailRegExpText = new RegExp(/^[A-Za-z0-9._+\-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.\-]+\.[A-Za-z]{2,6}$/gi);
                                    var valid_mail = mailRegExpText.test(mail.trim());
                                    return valid_mail;
                                },
                                EmailMatch       : function (email, email_confirm) {
                                    var mail = $(email)
                                        .value
                                        .trim();
                                    var mail_confirm = $(email_confirm)
                                        .value
                                        .trim();
                                    return (mail == mail_confirm);
                                },
                                InvalidCharacters: function (field, values, service) {
                                    var invalidCharactersRegExpText = new RegExp(/([^a-zA-Z0-9\-])+/gi);
                                    var tests = {
                                        c1: {
                                            expected_result: true,
                                            regexp         : invalidCharactersRegExpText
                                        }
                                    };
                                    switch (field) {
                                        case "ZipCode":
                                            tests = {
                                                c1: {
                                                    expected_result: true,
                                                    regexp         : new RegExp(/([^0-9\-])+/gi)
                                                }
                                            };
                                            if (oScope.sService == "TCYCA" || oScope.sService == "CJCA") {
                                                tests = {
                                                    c1: {
                                                        expected_result: true,
                                                        regexp         : new RegExp(/([^a-z0-9\s\-])+/gi)
                                                    }
                                                };
                                            }
                                            break;
                                        case "LastName":
                                            tests = {
                                                c1: {
                                                    expected_result: true,
                                                    regexp         : new RegExp(/([^a-zA-Z\s])+/gi)
                                                },
                                                c2: {
                                                    expected_result: true,
                                                    regexp         : new RegExp(/\w+\s{2,}\w+/gi)
                                                }
                                            };
                                            break;
                                        case "Name":
                                            tests = {
                                                c1: {
                                                    expected_result: true,
                                                    regexp         : new RegExp(/([^a-zA-Z\s])+/gi)
                                                },
                                                c2: {
                                                    expected_result: true,
                                                    regexp         : new RegExp(/\w+\s{2,}\w+/gi)
                                                }
                                            };
                                            break;
                                    }
                                    for (var i = 0; i < values.length; i += 1) {
                                        for (test in tests) {
                                            var ctest = tests[test];
                                            if (ctest.regexp.test(values[i]) == ctest.expected_result && values[i] !== "") {
                                                return true;
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                    return false;
                                },
                                InvalidLength    : function (text, range) {
                                    if (range === -1) {
                                        return false;
                                    }
                                    return !(text.length >= range[0] && text.length <= range[1]);
                                },
                                LastName         : function (name) {
                                    var nameRegExpText = new RegExp(/^\s?[a-zA-Z\s]+/gi);
                                    var filledRegExpText = new RegExp(/[a-zA-Z]+/gi);
                                    return (nameRegExpText.test(name) && filledRegExpText.test(name));
                                },
                                Name             : function (name) {
                                    var nameRegExpText = new RegExp(/^\s?[a-zA-Z\s]+/gi);
                                    var filledRegExpText = new RegExp(/[a-zA-Z]+/gi);
                                    return (nameRegExpText.test(name) && filledRegExpText.test(name));
                                },
                                ZipCode          : function (zipcode) {
                                    var zipcodeRegExpText = new RegExp(/^\d{5}([\-]\d{4})?$/);
                                    if (oScope.sService == "TCYCA" || oScope.sService == "CJCA") {
                                        zipcodeRegExpText = new RegExp(/[a-z]\d[a-z]|\d[a-z]\d/ig);
                                    }
                                    var zipcodetest = zipcodeRegExpText.test(zipcode);
                                    return zipcodetest;
                                }
                            };
                            var fields = [];
                            switch (this.sState) {
                                case module_states.SIGNUP:
                                    fields = [
                                        this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail + "|Email",
                                        this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMail + ";" + this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleMailConfirm + "|EmailMatch",
                                        this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleName + "|Name",
                                        this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleLastName + "|LastName",
                                        this.oPopupComponents.sSignupModuleZipCode + "|ZipCode"
                                    ];
                                    break;
                                case module_states.HP_WIDGET:
                                    fields = [this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail + "|Email"];
                                    break;
                                case module_states.SA_WIDGET:
                                    fields = [this.oWidgetComponents.sSignupModuleSubscribeMail + "|Email"];
                                    break;
                            }
                            for (var f = 0; f < fields.length; f += 1) {
                                var inst = fields[f].split(/\|/);
                                var errorCode = "";
                                var invalidField = "";
                                var invalidLength = "";
                                var validation_args = [];
                                var validLength = [2, 25];
                                switch (inst[1]) {
                                    case "Email":
                                        validation_args = [jQuery("#" + inst[0]).attr("value")];
                                        validLength     = [0, 60];
                                        errorCode       = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sBadMail;
                                        invalidLength   = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sLongMail;
                                        break;
                                    case "EmailMatch":
                                        validation_args = inst[0].split(/;/);
                                        errorCode       = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sSignupError;
                                        break;
                                    case "Name":
                                        validation_args = [jQuery("#" + inst[0]).attr("value")];
                                        errorCode       = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sEmptyFirstName;
                                        invalidField    = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sInvalidFirstName;
                                        invalidLength   = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sLongFirstName;
                                        break;
                                    case "LastName":
                                        validation_args = [jQuery("#" + inst[0]).attr("value")];
                                        errorCode       = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sEmptyLastName;
                                        invalidField    = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sInvalidLastName;
                                        invalidLength   = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sLongLastName;
                                        break;
                                    case "ZipCode":
                                        validation_args = [jQuery("#" + inst[0]).attr("value")];
                                        errorCode       = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sEmptyZip;
                                        invalidField    = this.oValidationErrorCodes.sInvalidZip;
                                        break;
                                }
                                if (invalidField !== "" && validate.InvalidCharacters.apply(this, [inst[1], validation_args])) {
                                    errors.push(invalidField);
                                } else {
                                    if (errorCode !== "" && !validate[inst[1]].apply(this, validation_args)) {
                                        errors.push(errorCode);
                                    } else {
                                        if (invalidLength !== "" && validate.InvalidLength.apply(this, [validation_args[0], validLength])) {
                                            errors.push(invalidLength);
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            return errors;
                        }
                    };
                    return new module();
                }
                return {
                    getPopupInstance : function (popup_config) {
                        if (!popup) {
                            popup = _Popup();
                            popup.setUp(popup_config);
                        }
                        return popup;
                    },
                    getSignUpInstance: function (module_config) {
                        if (!signup_module) {
                            signup_module = _SignupModule();
                            signup_module.setUp(module_config);
                        }
                        return signup_module;
                    }
                };
            })(); // .
            // *****END***** // The following js comes from:
            // http://i.travelpn.com/js/homepage.js //
            AdvancedSearch                                  = {};
            AdvancedSearch.OneWaySearchConfig               = {
                BasicSearchFiedls: {
                    adults               : "fo-adults",
                    arrival_dt           : "arrival_dt",
                    children             : "fo-minors",
                    departDateFlexibility: "ddate-flex",
                    departure_dt         : "departure_dt",
                    goingTo              : "fo-to",
                    leavingDate          : "fo-fromdate",
                    leavingFrom          : "fo-from",
