            (function (e) {
                e.widget("ui.menu", {
                    _create     : function () {
                        var a = this;
                        this
                            .element
                            .addClass("ui-menu ui-widget ui-widget-content ui-corner-all")
                            .attr({"aria-activedescendant": "ui-active-menuitem", role: "listbox"})
                            .click(function (b) {
                                if (e(b.target).closest(".ui-menu-item a").length) {
                                    b.preventDefault();
                                    a.select(b);
                                }
                            });
                        this.refresh();
                    },
                    activate    : function (a, b) {
                        this.deactivate();
                        if (this.hasScroll()) {
                            var f = b
                                    .offset()
                                    .top - this
                                    .element
                                    .offset()
                                    .top,
                                c = this
                                    .element
                                    .attr("scrollTop"),
                                d = this
                                    .element
                                    .height();
                            if (f < 0) {
                                this
                                    .element
                                    .attr("scrollTop", c + f);
                            } else {
                                f >= d && this
                                    .element
                                    .attr("scrollTop", c + f - d + b.height());
                            }
                        }
                        this.active = b
                            .eq(0)
                            .children("a")
                            .addClass("ui-state-hover")
                            .attr("id", "ui-active-menuitem")
                            .end();
                        this._trigger("focus", a, {item: b});
                    },
                    deactivate  : function () {
                        if (this.active) {
                            this
                                .active
                                .children("a")
                                .removeClass("ui-state-hover")
                                .removeAttr("id");
                            this._trigger("blur");
                            this.active = null;
                        }
                    },
                    first       : function () {
                        return this.active && !this
                            .active
                            .prevAll(".ui-menu-item")
                            .length;
                    },
                    hasScroll   : function () {
                        return this
                            .element
                            .height() < this
                            .element
                            .attr("scrollHeight");
                    },
                    last        : function () {
                        return this.active && !this
                            .active
                            .nextAll(".ui-menu-item")
                            .length;
                    },
                    move        : function (a, b, f) {
                        if (this.active) {
                            a = this
                                .active[a + "All"](".ui-menu-item")
                                .eq(0);
                            a.length
                                ? this.activate(f, a)
                                : this.activate(f, this.element.children(b));
                        } else {
                            this.activate(f, this.element.children(b));
                        }
                    },
                    next        : function (a) {
                        this.move("next", ".ui-menu-item:first", a);
                    },
                    nextPage    : function (a) {
                        if (this.hasScroll()) {
                            if (!this.active || this.last()) {
                                this.activate(a, this.element.children(".ui-menu-item:first"));
                            } else {
                                var b = this
                                        .active
                                        .offset()
                                        .top,
                                    f = this
                                        .element
                                        .height(),
                                    c = this
                                        .element
                                        .children(".ui-menu-item")
                                        .filter(function () {
                                            var d = e(this)
                                                .offset()
                                                .top - b - f + e(this).height();
                                            return d < 10 && d > -10;
                                        });
                                c.length || (c = this.element.children(".ui-menu-item:last"));
                                this.activate(a, c);
                            } else {
                                this.activate(a, this.element.children(".ui-menu-item").filter(!this.active || this.last()
                                    ? ":first"
                                    : ":last"));
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    previous    : function (a) {
                        this.move("prev", ".ui-menu-item:last", a);
                    },
                    previousPage: function (a) {
                        if (this.hasScroll()) {
                            if (!this.active || this.first()) {
                                this.activate(a, this.element.children(".ui-menu-item:last"));
                            } else {
                                var b = this
                                        .active
                                        .offset()
                                        .top,
                                    f = this
                                        .element
                                        .height();
                                result = this
                                    .element
                                    .children(".ui-menu-item")
                                    .filter(function () {
                                        var c = e(this)
                                            .offset()
                                            .top - b + f - e(this).height();
                                        return c < 10 && c > -10;
                                    });
                                result.length || (result = this.element.children(".ui-menu-item:first"));
                                this.activate(a, result);
                            } else {
                                this.activate(a, this.element.children(".ui-menu-item").filter(!this.active || this.first()
                                    ? ":last"
                                    : ":first"));
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    refresh     : function () {
                        var a = this;
                        this
                            .element
                            .children("li:not(.ui-menu-item):has(a)")
                            .addClass("ui-menu-item")
                            .attr("role", "menuitem")
                            .children("a")
                            .addClass("ui-corner-all")
                            .attr("tabindex", -1)
                            .mouseenter(function (b) {
                                a.activate(b, e(this).parent());
                            })
                            .mouseleave(function () {
                                a.deactivate();
                            });
                    },
                    select      : function (a) {
                        this._trigger("selected", a, {item: this.active});
                    }
                });
            })(jQuery);
            // . *****END***** // The following js comes from:
            // http://i.travelpn.com/js/cookie.js //
            jQuery.cookie            = function (name, value, options) {
                if (typeof value != "undefined") {
                    options = options || {};
                    if (value === null) {
                        value           = "";
                        options.expires = -1;
                    }
                    var expires = "";
                    if (options.expires && (typeof options.expires == "number" || options.expires.toUTCString)) {
                        var date;
                        if (typeof options.expires == "number") {
                            date = new Date();
                            date.setTime(date.getTime() + (options.expires * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                        } else {
                            date = options.expires;
                        }
                        expires = "; expires=" + date.toUTCString();
                    }
                    var path = options.path
                        ? "; path=" + (options.path)
                        : "";
                    var domain = options.domain
                        ? "; domain=" + (options.domain)
                        : "";
                    var secure = options.secure
                        ? "; secure"
                        : "";
                    document.cookie = [
                        name,
                        "=",
                        encodeURIComponent(value),
                        expires,
                        path,
                        domain,
                        secure
                    ].join("");
                } else {
                    var cookieValue = null;
                    if (document.cookie && document.cookie != "") {
                        var cookies = document
                            .cookie
                            .split(";");
                        for (var i = 0; i < cookies.length; i += 1) {
                            var cookie = jQuery.trim(cookies[i]);
                            if (cookie.substring(0, name.length + 1) == (name + "=")) {
                                cookieValue = decodeURIComponent(cookie.substring(name.length + 1));
                                break;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    return cookieValue;
                }
            };
            jQuery.areCookiesEnabled = function () {
                var cookieEnabled = (navigator.cookieEnabled)
                    ? true
                    : false;
                if (typeof navigator.cookieEnabled == "undefined" && !cookieEnabled) {
                    document.cookie = "testcookie";
                    cookieEnabled   = (document.cookie.indexOf("testcookie") != -1)
                        ? true
                        : false;
                }
                return (cookieEnabled);
            }; // .
            // *****END***** // The following js comes from:
            // http://i.travelpn.com/js/autocomplete.js //
            (function ($) {
                jQuery._autocomplete               = function (config) {
                    try {
                        var elementId                  = config.elementId,
                            selectCallback             = config.selectCallback || null,
                            minLength                  = config.minLength || 3,
                            source                     = config.source || "gls",
                            url                        = config.url || null,
                            lob                        = config.LOB || null,
                            glsResolveTo               = config.glsResolveTo || null,
                            locationType               = config.locationType,
                            numResultsInServiceRequest = config.numResultsInServiceRequest || 100,
                            numberOfResultsDisplay     = config.numberOfResultsDisplay || 100,
                            displayIcons               = config.displayIcons || false,
                            customParams               = config.customParams || {},
                            labelConfig                = config.labelConfig || {},
                            ret                        = [],
                            keyboardFocus              = false,
                            default_geo_location       = "32.767300|-96.777702|Dallas|TX|75261|US",
                            geo_location               = ($.cookie("TVLY_GEO") === null)
                                ? default_geo_location
                                : $.cookie("TVLY_GEO"),
                            arr_geo_location           = geo_location.split("|"),
                            userLatitude               = parseFloat(arr_geo_location[0]),
                            userLongitude              = parseFloat(arr_geo_location[1]),
                            userCity                   = arr_geo_location[2],
                            userStateCode              = arr_geo_location[3],
                            userZipCode                = arr_geo_location[4],
                            userCountryCode            = arr_geo_location[5];
                        jQuery
                            ._autocomplete
                            .customRender({displayIcons: displayIcons, source: source});
                        $("#" + elementId).focus(function () {
                            var displayLabel = $("#" + elementId).attr("display-label");
                            $(this).val(displayLabel != undefined
                                ? displayLabel
                                : "");
                        });
                        $("#" + elementId).blur(function () {
                            $("#" + elementId).removeAttr("display-label");
                        });
                        $("#" + elementId).autocomplete({
                            focus    : function (evt, ui) {
                                return false;
                            },
                            minLength: minLength,
                            select   : function (evt, ui) {
                                if (ui != undefined && ui.item != undefined && ui.item.value != undefined) {
                                    $("#" + elementId).attr("display-label", ui.item.value);
                                    $("#" + elementId).data("value", ui.item.value);
                                }
                                if ($.isFunction(selectCallback)) {
                                    selectCallback(ui.item, elementId);
                                }
                            },
                            source   : function (request, response) {
                                var inputString = request.term;
                                config.inputString = inputString;
                                if (request.term in jQuery._autocomplete.cache) {
                                    var height = (jQuery._autocomplete.cache[request.term].length < 11)
                                        ? jQuery._autocomplete.cache[request.term].length * 22
                                        : 270;
                                    $("ul.ui-autocomplete").css({height: height});
                                    response(jQuery._autocomplete.cache[request.term]);
                                    return;
                                }
                                if (typeof(config.source) !== "undefined" && config.source === "google") {
                                    config.params.q = request.term;
                                    config.response = response;
                                    ret             = jQuery
                                        ._autocomplete
                                        .getData(config);
                                } else {
                                    ret = jQuery
                                        ._autocomplete
                                        .getGLSData({
                                            customParams              : customParams,
                                            displayIcons              : displayIcons,
                                            glsResolveTo              : glsResolveTo,
                                            inputString               : inputString,
                                            labelConfig               : labelConfig,
                                            LOB                       : lob,
                                            locationType              : locationType,
                                            numberOfResultsDisplay    : numberOfResultsDisplay,
                                            numResultsInServiceRequest: numResultsInServiceRequest,
                                            response                  : response,
                                            url                       : url,
                                            userLatitude              : userLatitude,
                                            userLongitude             : userLongitude
                                        });
                                }
                            }
                        });
                    } catch (ex) {
                        if (typeof(console) !== "undefined" && typeof(console.log) !== "undefined") {
                            console.log("jQuery._autocomplete error", ex);
                        }
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.getData       = function (config) {
                    try {
                        var ret,
                            opts = {
                                data    : config.params,
                                dataType: config.dataType,
                                success : function (data) {
                                    config.callback(data, config);
                                    jQuery._autocomplete.cache[config.inputString] = ret;
                                },
                                type    : "GET",
                                url     : config.url
                            };
                        $.ajax(opts);
                    } catch (ex) {
                        if (typeof(console) !== "undefined" && typeof(console.log) !== "undefined") {
                            console.log("jQuery._autocomplete.getData error", ex);
                        }
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.sortResults   = {
                    AIR: function (config, results) {
                        return results.sort(jQuery._autocomplete.sorter[config.LOB]);
                    },
                    HOT: function (config, results) {
                        var results = results.sort(jQuery._autocomplete.sorter[config.LOB]);
                        var tempSort = {};
                        var aux = [];
                        for (var key in results) {
                            var cityName = results[key].cityName;
                            if (typeof tempSort[cityName] !== "object") {
                                tempSort[cityName] = [];
                                aux.push(cityName);
                            }
                            tempSort[cityName].push(results[key]);
                        }
                        var finalSort = [];
                        var auxLength = (aux.length == 1)
                            ? 2
                            : aux.length;
                        for (var i = 0; i < auxLength - 1; i += 1) {
                            var index = aux[i];
                            for (var x = 0; x < tempSort[index].length; x += 1) {
                                finalSort.push(tempSort[index][x]);
                            }
                        }
                        return finalSort;
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.sorter        = {
                    AIR: function (a, b) {
                        var sortValue        = 0,
                            leftCountryCode  = a.countryCode,
                            rightCountryCode = b.countryCode,
                            leftRank         = parseInt(a.rank),
                            rightRank        = parseInt(b.rank),
                            leftDistance     = parseFloat(a.distance),
                            rightDistance    = parseFloat(b.distance);
                        if (leftCountryCode !== "US" && rightCountryCode === "US") {
                            sortValue = 1;
                        } else {
                            if (leftCountryCode === "US" && rightCountryCode !== "US") {
                                sortValue = -1;
                            } else {
                                if (isNaN(rightRank) || isNaN(leftRank)) {
                                    sortValue = 0;
                                } else {
                                    sortValue = rightRank - leftRank;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        if (sortValue === 0) {
                            if (isNaN(leftDistance) || isNaN(rightDistance)) {
                                sortValue = 0;
                            } else {
                                sortValue = leftDistance - rightDistance;
                            }
                        }
                        return sortValue;
                    },
                    HOT: function (a, b) {
                        var ret = 0;
                        if (isNaN(a.rank) || isNaN(b.rank)) {
                            ret = 0;
                        } else {
                            ret = b.rank - a.rank;
                        }
                        return ret;
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.getGLSData    = function (config) {
                    try {
                        var url = config.url;
                        var customParams = config.customParams || {};
                        var extraParams = {
                            inputString : config.inputString,
                            numRequested: config.numResultsInServiceRequest,
                            resolveTo   : (typeof(config.glsResolveTo) === "string")
                                ? config.glsResolveTo
                                : config.LOB
                        };
                        var params = jQuery.extend({}, customParams, extraParams);
                        var ret;
                        $.ajax({
                            data    : params,
                            dataType: "xml",
                            success : function (data) {
                                json = $("AutoCompleteResults LocationInfo", data).map(function () {
                                    if ($.inArray($("LocationType", this).text(), config.locationType) >= 0) {
                                        return {
                                            CityCode         : $("CityCode", this).text(),
                                            CityName         : $("CityName", this).text(),
                                            CountryCode      : $("CountryCode", this).text(),
                                            CountryName      : $("CountryName", this).text(),
                                            Distance         : jQuery
                                                ._autocomplete
                                                .getDistance(config.userLatitude, config.userLongitude, $("Latitude", this).text(), $("Longitude", this).text()),
                                            Latitude         : $("Latitude", this).text(),
                                            LocationCode     : ($("LocationCode", this).length)
                                                ? $("LocationCode", this).text()
                                                : $("CityCode", this).text(),
                                            LocationId       : $(this).attr("LocationId"),
                                            LocationName     : $("LocationName", this).text(),
                                            LocationType     : $("LocationType", this).text(),
                                            Longitude        : $("Longitude", this).text(),
                                            Rank             : $("Rank", this).text(),
                                            StateProvinceCode: $("StateProvinceCode", this).text(),
                                            StateProvinceName: $("StateProvinceName", this).text()
                                        };
                                    } else {
                                        return null;
                                    }
                                });
                                var formatFunc = jQuery._autocomplete.GLSFormatting[config.LOB];
                                var mappedData = json.map(function () {
                                    return formatFunc(this, config);
                                });
                                var filteredData = jQuery._autocomplete.filterFuncs[config.LOB](config, mappedData);
                                var sortedData = jQuery._autocomplete.sortResults[config.LOB](config, filteredData);
                                ret = sortedData.slice(0, config.numberOfResultsDisplay);
                                for (var x = 0; x < ret.length; x += 1) {
                                    ret[x].listpos = x;
                                }
                                var height = (ret.length < 11)
                                    ? ret.length * 22
                                    : 270;
                                $("ul.ui-autocomplete").css({height: height});
                                config.response(ret);
                                jQuery._autocomplete.cache[config.inputString] = ret;
                            },
                            type    : "GET",
                            url     : url
                        });
                    } catch (ex) {
                        if (typeof(console) !== "undefined" && typeof(console.log) !== "undefined") {
                            console.log("jQuery._autocomplete.parseGLS error", ex);
                        }
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.customRender  = function (config) {
                    if (config.source === "gls") {
                        jQuery
                            ._autocomplete
                            .glsRender(config);
                    } else {
                        jQuery
                            ._autocomplete
                            .defaultRender(config);
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.defaultRender = function (config) {
                    $.ui.autocomplete.prototype._renderItem = function (ul, item) {
                        var re            = new RegExp(this.term, "ig"),
                            matchPosition = item
                                .value
                                .search(re),
                            searchTerm    = item
                                .value
                                .split(re),
                            result        = item
                                .value
                                .replace(re, "<span class='highlightCharacters'>" + item.value.substring(matchPosition, matchPosition + this.term.length) + "</span>");
                        return $("<li></li>").addClass((config.displayIcons === true)
                            ? "autocomplete-lob-icon"
                                : "")
                            .data("item.autocomplete", item)
                            .append("<a>" + result + "</a>")
                            .appendTo(ul);
                    };
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.glsRender     = function (config) {
                    $.ui.autocomplete.prototype._renderItem = function (ul, item) {
                        var re            = new RegExp(this.term, "ig"),
                            matchPosition = item
                                .value
                                .search(re),
                            searchTerm    = item
                                .value
                                .split(re),
                            result        = item
                                .value
                                .replace(re, "<span class='highlightCharacters'>" + item.value.substring(matchPosition, matchPosition + this.term.length) + "</span>");
                        return $("<li></li>").addClass((item.type === "ARP")
                            ? "airline"
                            : "city").addClass((config.displayIcons === true)
                            ? "autocomplete-lob-icon"
                                : "")
                            .data("item.autocomplete", item)
                            .append("<a>" + item.label + "</a>")
                            .appendTo(ul);
                    };
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.cache         = {};
                jQuery._autocomplete.GLSFormatting = {
                    AIR: function (thisRef, configObj) {
                        var cityName          = $.trim(thisRef.CityName),
                            locationName      = $.trim(thisRef.LocationName),
                            stateProvinceCode = $.trim(thisRef.StateProvinceCode),
                            locationId        = $.trim(thisRef.LocationId),
                            locationCode      = $.trim(thisRef.LocationCode),
                            locationType      = $.trim(thisRef.LocationType),
                            countryCode       = $.trim(thisRef.CountryCode),
                            rank              = parseInt($.trim(thisRef.Rank)),
                            countryName       = $.trim(thisRef.CountryName),
                            distance          = $.trim(thisRef.Distance);
                        var labelConfig = configObj.labelConfig || {};
                        var value = labelConfig[locationType];
                        if (value == null) {
                            value = "${locationName}${cityName}${stateProvinceCode}${countryName}${locationCode}";
                        }
                        value = value.replace("${locationName}", locationName);
                        value = value.replace("${cityName}", ((cityName !== locationName)
                            ? (", " + cityName)
                            : ""));
                        value = value.replace("${stateProvinceCode}", ((stateProvinceCode !== "")
                            ? (", " + stateProvinceCode)
                            : ""));
                        value = value.replace("${countryName}", ((countryName !== "" && countryCode !== "US")
                            ? (", " + countryName)
                            : ""));
                        value = value.replace("${locationType}", ((locationType !== "")
                            ? (", " + locationType)
                            : ""));
                        value = value.replace("${locationCode}", ((locationCode !== "")
                            ? (" (" + locationCode + ")")
                            : ""));
                        return {
                            cityName         : cityName,
                            countryCode      : countryCode,
                            countryName      : countryName,
                            distance         : distance,
                            inputString      : configObj.inputString,
                            label            : value,
                            locationCode     : locationCode,
                            locationId       : locationId,
                            locationName     : locationName,
                            locationType     : locationType,
                            rank             : rank,
                            stateProvinceCode: stateProvinceCode,
                            value            : locationCode
                        };
                    },
                    HOT: function (thisRef, configObj) {
                        var hotsFormat = jQuery
                            ._autocomplete
                            .GLSFormatting
                            .AIR(thisRef, configObj);
                        hotsFormat.value       = hotsFormat.label;
                        hotsFormat.inputString = configObj.inputString;
                        return hotsFormat;
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.filterFuncs   = {
                    AIR: function (configObj, mappedData) {
                        var qCityCodesToFilter = ["QDF", "QHO"];
                        var allAirportsToFilter = ["DFW", "HOU"];
                        function filterItem(theItem) {
                            var qCityCodeData = (jQuery.inArray(theItem.locationCode, qCityCodesToFilter) >= 0);
                            if (qCityCodeData) {
                                return true;
                            }
                            if (theItem.locationType == "CTY") {
                                return (jQuery.inArray(theItem.locationCode, allAirportsToFilter) >= 0);
                            }
                            return false;
                        }
                        var resultArray = [];
                        if (mappedData != null) {
                            for (var i = 0; i < mappedData.length; i += 1) {
                                if (!filterItem(mappedData[i])) {
                                    resultArray.push(mappedData[i]);
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        return resultArray;
                    },
                    HOT: function (configObj, mappedData) {
                        var resultArray = [];
                        mainLoop : for (var i = 0; i < mappedData.length; i += 1) {
                            if (resultArray.length >= 1) {
                                for (var x = 0; x < resultArray.length; x += 1) {
                                    if (mappedData[i]["locationId"] == resultArray[x]["locationId"]) {
                                        continue mainLoop;
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            resultArray.push(mappedData[i]);
                        }
                        return resultArray;
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.addCustomData = {
                    AIR: function (json) {
                        var nycFlag = false;
                        var newarkFlag = false;
                        $.each(json, function (i, val) {
                            if (!nycFlag && val.CityName == "New York") {
                                nycFlag = true;
                            }
                            if (nycFlag && val.CityName == "Newark") {
                                newarkFlag = true;
                            }
                        });
                        if (nycFlag && !newarkFlag) {
                            var newark = {
                                CityCode        : "NYC",
                                CityName        : "Newark",
                                CountryCode     : "US",
                                CountryName     : "United States",
                                Latitude        : "40.69222",
                                LocationCode    : "EWR",
                                LocationName    : "Newark Liberty International Airport",
                                LocationType    : "ARP",
                                Longitude       : "-74.16861",
                                Rank            : "21",
                                StateProviceCode: "NJ",
                                StateProviceName: "New Jersey"
                            };
                            json.push(newark);
                        }
                    },
                    HOT: function (json) {
                        return true;
                    }
                };
                jQuery._autocomplete.getDistance   = function (lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2, unit) {
                    lat1 = parseFloat(lat1);
                    lat2 = parseFloat(lat2);
                    lon1 = parseFloat(lon1);
                    lon2 = parseFloat(lon2);
                    var rLat1    = Math.PI * (lat1 / 180),
                        rLat2    = Math.PI * (lat2 / 180),
                        rLon1    = Math.PI * (lon1 / 180),
                        rLon2    = Math.PI * (lon2 / 180),
                        radius1  = Math.PI * (lat1 / 180),
                        theta    = lon1 - lon2,
                        rTheta   = Math.PI * (theta / 180),
                        distance = (Math.sin(rLat1) * Math.sin(rLat2)) + (Math.cos(rLat1) * Math.cos(rLat2)) * Math.cos(rTheta);
                    distance = Math.acos(distance);
                    distance = distance * 180 / Math.PI;
                    distance = distance * 60 * 1.1515;
                    if (unit === "KM") {
                        distance = distance * 1.609344;
                    }
                    if (unit === "NM") {
                        distance = distance * 0.8684;
                    }
                    return distance + "";
                };
            })(jQuery); // .
            // *****END***** // . *****END***** //
        </script>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            jQuery(function () {
                new jQuery
                    .tvly
                    .Cannonball({cruiseScript: "http://i.travelpn.com.edgesuite.net/js/jquery.cb.cruise-1.0.js"});

                jQuery("input#fh-from, input#fh-to, input#fo-from, input#fo-to, input#co-to").val("");

                var AutoCompleteOptions = {
                    customParams              : {
                        channel: "TVLY",
                        client : "FRONT_DOOR_HTL",
                        locale : "en_US"
                    },
                    displayIcons              : false,
                    glsResolveTo              : "CTY,AIR",
                    labelConfig               : {
                        ARP: "${locationName}${cityName}${stateProvinceCode}${countryName}${locationCode}",
                        CTY: "${locationName}${cityName}${stateProvinceCode}${countryName}"
                    },
                    LOB                       : "HOT",
                    locationType              : [
                        "ARP", "CTY"
                    ],
                    numberOfResultsDisplay    : 10,
                    numResultsInServiceRequest: 40,
                    selectCallback            : function (item, elementId) {
                        var _to  = $("#" + elementId)
                                .attr("id")
                                .match("-to"),
                            _l,
                            _cty = $("#" + elementId)
                                .attr("class")
                                .match("-city");
                        var typedDestination = item.inputString;
                        switch (item.locationType) {
                            case "ARP":
                                var gaDestination = item.locationCode;
                                $("#" + elementId).attr("display-label", item.locationCode);
                                switch (_to) {
                                    case null:
                                        $(".cb-from").val(item.locationCode);
                                        $(".cb-from-city").val(item.locationCode);
                                        break;
                                    default:
                                        $(".cb-to").val(item.locationCode);
                                        $(".cb-to-city").val(item.locationCode);
                                        $(".cb-country", ".cannonball")
                                            .val(item.countryCode)
                                            .trigger("change");
                                        $(".cb-state", ".cannonball").val(item.stateProvinceCode);
                                }
                                break;
                            case "CTY":
                                _l = item.cityName;
                                var gaDestination = _l;
                                if (item.stateProvinceCode != "") {
                                    _l += "," + item.stateProvinceCode;
                                }
                                if (item.countryCode != "US") {
                                    _l += "," + item.countryCode;
                                }
                                switch (_to) {
                                    case null:
                                        $(".cb-from").val(_l);
                                        $(".cb-from-city").val(item.cityName);
                                        break;
                                    default:
                                        $(".cb-to").val(_l);
                                        $(".cb-to-city").val(item.cityName);
                                        $(".cb-country", ".cannonball")
                                            .val(item.countryCode)
                                            .trigger("change");
                                        $(".cb-state", ".cannonball").val(item.stateProvinceCode);
                                }
                                switch (_cty) {
                                    case null:
                                        $("#" + elementId).attr("display-label", _l);
                                        break;
                                    default:
                                        $("#" + elementId).attr("display-label", item.cityName);
                                }
                                break;
                        }
                        switch (elementId) {
                            case "ho-to":
                                _gaq.push([
                                    "_trackEvent", "ac:HP", "ac:HP|hotel_only|DestinationAutoFill", gaDestination + "|" + item.listpos + "|" + typedDestination
                                ]);
                                break;
                            case "hcx-to":
                                _gaq.push([
                                    "_trackEvent", "ac:HP", "ac:HP|hotel+car|DestinationAutoFill", gaDestination + "|" + item.listpos + "|" + typedDestination
                                ]);
                                break;
                        }
                    },
                    source                    : "gls",
                    url                       : "/servicegateway/shopping-svcs/global-location-svc-autocomplete-1.0/services/auto" +
                                                    "complete"
                };

                jQuery._autocomplete(jQuery.extend({}, AutoCompleteOptions, {elementId: "ho-to"}));
                jQuery._autocomplete(jQuery.extend({}, AutoCompleteOptions, {elementId: "hcx-to"}));
                jQuery("#ho-to, #hcx-to").bind("autocompleteselect", false);
            });
        </script>


        <script id="dealsTemplate" type="text/x-jquery-tmpl">
            <tr>
                <td class="deal-type" scope="row">${Type}</td>
                <td class="deal-description">
                    <a
                        href="http://vacations.travelocity.com/merchandising/offers/LandingPage.do?destinationId=${DestinationId}&hotelSortOrder=picks&airportCode=${AirportCode}&locLink=GLB_HOMEPAGE|DEALSWIDGET">${Description}</a>
                </td>
                <td class="deal-price">
                    <a
                        href="http://vacations.travelocity.com/merchandising/offers/LandingPage.do?destinationId=${DestinationId}&hotelSortOrder=picks&airportCode=${AirportCode}&locLink=GLB_HOMEPAGE|DEALSWIDGET">
                        <span>${PriceDiscount}</span>
                    </a>
                </td>
                <td class="deal-price-type">${PriceDetail}</td>
            </tr>
        </script>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            if ($.browser.msie && $.browser.version == "6.0") {
                var modalID = "ie6-modal-container";
                var messageID = "ie6-message";
                var closeBtnClass = "close";

                jQuery("body").append(jQuery("<div></div>").attr("id", modalID));
                jQuery("#" + modalID).css("display", "block");
                jQuery("#" + modalID).css("height", window.innerHeight);
                document.body.scroll = "no";

                jQuery.ajax({
                    data   : "site=TRAVELOCITY",
                    success: function (data) {
                        jQuery("#" + modalID).after(data);
                        jQuery("#" + messageID).css("display", "block");
                        jQuery("." + closeBtnClass).each(function () {
                            jQuery(this)
                                .click(function (e) {
                                    e.preventDefault();
                                    jQuery("body select").each(function () {
                                        jQuery(this).css("visibility", "visible");
                                    });
                                    document.body.scroll = "yes";
                                    jQuery("#" + modalID).remove();
                                    jQuery("#" + messageID).remove();
                                });
                        });
                    },
                    url    : "/ie6-message"
                });
                jQuery("body select").each(function () {
                    jQuery(this).css("visibility", "hidden");
                });
            }
        </script>
    </body>

</html>
